    "hash_1b8da665e51b20f": "^1Marlton: ^7Remember this, Stu, the next time you want to call me a geek, or a loser, or... I'm already starting to regret this.",
    "hash_207c3129488d5a3": "^1Marlton: ^7Bullets to the brain do indeed continue to be effective, Misty.",
