    "hash_2123c129491f7c3": "^1Russman: ^7Good shot, missy! I mean Misty.",
    "hash_21471313b449ab5": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7So hungry. Why is there never a pack-a-lunch? Wait -- have I asked this already?",
    "hash_21472313b449c68": "^1Misty: ^7All right, no deadheads better come along right now.",
    "hash_21473313b449e1b": "^1Marlton: ^7I can't tell if I'm shivering from cold or trembling with fear. It's a thin line.",
    "hash_21e7c313b4d01eb": "^1Russman: ^7I keep expectin' warm cookies to pop outta this thing. Mmmm. Cookies.",
    "hash_260c543ab263fac": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Who left these lying around? I'm sure they won't miss 'em.",
    "hash_260cb43ab2649de": "^1Marlton: ^7Thrown hard enough, even a snowball can kill. I hope.",
    "hash_260cc43ab264b91": "^1Misty: ^7Yeah! So cold out here one of these could shatter a freakbag.",
    "hash_2644a43ab295782": "^1Russman: ^7Snowballs is better than no balls...right, Marlton?",
    "hash_28a50820f423cfc": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7These things seem to have a mind of their own. Which is more'n I can say for Misty...",
    "hash_28a56820f42472e": "^1Marlton: ^7Now, this? This is just crude, brute force. Don't get me started about the mess...",
    "hash_28a57820f4248e1": "^1Misty: ^7Little woman. Big boom. Nuff said.",
