    "hash_50d83a4f11ad9d8": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to claim the Agarthan Device",
    "hash_52a2a11e9831b98": "^1Russman: ^7Here comes the deadhead shock troops. Heh.",
    "hash_534a111e98c3a52": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Might want to steer clear of the electric maggot-bags.",
    "hash_534a311e98c3db8": "^1Marlton: ^7Fascinating! A reanimate with its own electromagnetic field.",
    "hash_534a411e98c3f6b": "^1Misty: ^7Great. Gotta come up with a name for these guys. How about Ol' Sparky? Dynamo Deadhead? Hmm... We'll keep trying.",
    "hash_553c8d3d48c0a30": "^1Misty: ^7Definitely gotta watch where I point this thing.",
    "hash_553c9d3d48c0be3": "^1Marlton: ^7The pen-knife is mightier than the sword!",
    "hash_553d7d3d48c23ad": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7This is some cutting-edge stuff. Ha! Y'hear what I said?",
    "hash_55e42d3d4952e03": "^1Russman: ^7I seen it all now! Maybe. No. Probably not.",
    "hash_55fc334ee6b2aa4": "^1Russman: ^7Russman's gonna pass on this. Up for grabs, y'all!",
    "hash_5631c9bf840cfa1": "^1Misty: ^7You know the phrase \"out of the frying pan, into the fire\"? Kinda did something similar here. Nice work, Stooly.",
    "hash_56a3234ee743bc6": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Anybody want this? At least my money won't go to waste.",
    "hash_56a3c34ee744cc4": "^1Marlton: ^7Not for me, but no sense letting it go to waste.",
    "hash_56a3d34ee744e77": "^1Misty: ^7Hard pass. Who else can use this? Anyone?",
