    "hash_7f5464b25d90d8c": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 for Part",
    "hash_84866323232ca2f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Oh, hang on...I misunderstood! I thought you were accusing me of being one of those fools who...who actually consume the FLESH?!",
    "hash_86f1462b5071047": "^1Misty: ^7Who the heck came up with a way to refine that 115 crap? Someone with too much time on their hands and not enough sense -- that's who.",
    "hash_87115f5e3c24bd6": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to view the dynamite location on the map",
    "hash_88c0dac3d89bf65": "^1Russman: ^7Russman don't ask for much, but it's nice when he gets it.",
    "hash_88f8bac3d8ccb56": "^1Misty: ^7Aaaalllllright!!",
    "hash_88f8cac3d8ccd09": "^1Marlton: ^7I knew I was right. I usually am.",
    "hash_89006ff7685100a": "^1Russman: ^7Adventure?! Russman ain't on no adventure! Russman's tryin' to stay alive! Dang. How can a boy with as many fancy words as you pick such a bad one to describe the stuff we been dealin' with?!!",
    "hash_8be467a4eee2c70": "^1Misty: ^7I may not like ya that much, but you're still better company than the dead-heads.",
    "hash_8be477a4eee2e23": "^1Marlton: ^7So. You still think I'm a useless \"pencil-neck\"? Yes, of course, you do...",
    "hash_8c8c07a4ef75043": "^1Russman: ^7Uh-uh, my friend. No way you're leavin' Russman ta fend for himself.",
    "hash_8cd8be8f2fc7c7c": "^1Hermit: ^7<sing \"La\" in the note of A>",
    "hash_8d0506ba1813654": "^1Russman: ^7I been around a lot longer than you, boy. Back at Broken Arrow, we wrote the BOOK on inter-dimensional time travel! It wasn't a very good book -- too many inaccuracies -- but we still wrote it!",
    "hash_8f27db491cedab4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Holy crow! I think I just wet myself.",
    "hash_8f998ff1247e539": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Coulda used this to clean my room in high school! Kidding, of course, I never clean anything.",
    "hash_8f9a1ff1247f484": "^1Misty: ^7Back off, slackjaws! An' I mean all the way back!",
    "hash_8f9a2ff1247f637": "^1Marlton: ^7A concussive, atmospheric pressure-wave. Brilliant!",
    "hash_8fa327d7b67d732": "^1Marlton: ^7A packed gun in the hand is worth two in the...where am I going with this?",
    "hash_8fa337d7b67d8e5": "^1Misty: ^7Gotta move now. Standin' still's what gets ya killed.",
    "hash_8fda17d7b6ac9a6": "^1Russman: ^7Come on, gun. We're movin' up in the world.",
    "hash_903abff12505a07": "^1Russman: ^7Make a wish and blow 'em out!",
    "hash_907ba2d4233282c": "^1Russman: ^7So was this ground zero for the slackjaw apocalypse?",
    "hash_911c32d423b8bfc": "^1Marlton: ^7I do not subscribe to superstitious notions, but if any place was ever cursed, this is it.",
    "hash_911c42d423b8daf": "^1Misty: ^7Stuhlinger, tell me your German pal didn't dream up this place.",
    "hash_911c92d423b962e": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Yikes. There's still people floating in those tanks. Well, ex-people, anyway...",
    "hash_9162184ef7f0220": "Get to the Beach!",
    "hash_933eae610b5ce60": "^1Russman: ^7Russman knows how to dance. Now where's my next partner...?",
    "hash_933f6d5c85adbdd": "^1Russman: ^7I wonder if the boathouse got wrecked by the walkin' meat-sacks, or if the Russkies just can't build a decent shack!",
    "hash_9342207f387ef68": "�%�hQ���/���\v\r^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hey, brain-buddy. What if I just hole up in the boathouse until things die down around here?",
    "hash_9375fd5c85dc41f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hey, brain-buddy. What if I just hole up in the boathouse until things die down around here?",
    "hash_93764d5c85dcc9e": "^1Misty: ^7I used to bartend at a dive called The Boathouse. If the guys there were fish, you'd throw 'em all back.",
    "hash_93765d5c85dce51": "^1Marlton: ^7Not much room in the boathouse. Might've made it cozy and warm, but I'm not getting cozy with reanimates.",
    "hash_93df3e610be3230": "^1Marlton: ^7This is just way too...intimate.",
    "hash_93df4e610be33e3": "^1Misty: ^7Hey, you took a poke at me, so...",
    "hash_93e01e610be49fa": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7What a waste of flesh...uh...no.",
    "hash_9771f361adc7444": "^1Misty: ^7The Box pulled a runner with my money. Dang, that burns my butt!",
    "zm_orange/location_docks": "Docks",
    "hash_9af968cebf182d2": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 to place Facility Gearbox",
    "hash_9b953314ab9ca3c": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Wheeeeeee!",
    "hash_9b959314ab9d46e": "^1Marlton: ^7Aieeeeeeee!",
    "hash_9b95a314ab9d621": "^1Misty: ^7Yahhhhhhhh!",
    "hash_9bcd8314abce212": "^1Russman: ^7Sonovaguuuuun!",
    "hash_9d411b0c9bd3432": "^1Marlton: ^7However this box functions, it's less a matter of physics than parapsychology.",
    "hash_9d412b0c9bd35e5": "^1Misty: ^7Yes! I always wanted a music box. Even if it had a scary ghost-girl inside. I'm not even joking!",
    "hash_9d413b0c9bd3798": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7It starts with haunted music boxes, but where does it stop? Scary antique dolls? Cursed board games? Cannibalism? Uh, strike that last one!",
    "hash_9d5bd02ee324610": "^1Russman: ^7Them scum-suckers sure seem interested in Misty. No accountin' for taste, I guess.",
    "hash_9d780b0c9c026a6": "^1Russman: ^7You know what song this music box plays? It's called \"Russman's Revenge.\"",
    "hash_9dfc602ee3aa9e0": "^1Marlton: ^7Watch it, Misty -- they're on your six! And your twelve! And, uh, all around your clock...!",
    "hash_9dfd402ee3ac1aa": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Somebody help Misty before they finish swarming her!",
    "hash_9f745ddeed64a65": "^1Nikolai: ^7Hello, team! You fight well for civilians. Keep up and Agarthan Device is yours for certain!",
    "hash_a16694afd0ec5d5": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7The bridge -- the brains of the ship. Located on the ass-end of the ship. Because irony!",
    "hash_a166a4afd0ec788": "^1Misty: ^7This is where they drive the boat, right? What do they call it? The wheelhouse? The bridge?",
    "hash_a166b4afd0ec93b": "^1Marlton: ^7Ship's command center is up here. One might surmise that it harbors something important.",
    "hash_a1a1117f1b670e5": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Fair enough, brain-box. I didn't mean to snap at you. I'm just a little on edge because of...you know...things.",
    "hash_a20744afd172d0b": "^1Russman: ^7A sun deck? On a Russkie arctic trawler? *chuckles* That's useless as a screen door on a submarine.",
    "hash_a2765ba6a6e49fb": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 for Wunderwaffe DG-Scharfschütze",
