    "hash_cc39791c7fdf965": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Misty are you stupid?! Get out of there!",
    "hash_cc39991c7fdfccb": "^1Marlton: ^7Misty, no! They're all around you!",
    "hash_cce2291c8073a1b": "^1Russman: ^7Young lady, you are about to get dogpiled.",
    "hash_d0b19e325d03cb9": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Fine, fine, give it here. Thanks for the extra five minutes of life this'll give me...",
    "hash_d0b22e325d04c04": "^1Misty: ^7What did the walking corpse say to the shotgun? Nothing. Slackjaws can't talk, silly.",
    "hash_d0b23e325d04db7": "^1Marlton: ^7Truth be told, I think shotguns are a bit...\"common\" for an intellect such as mine.",
    "hash_d152ce325d8b187": "^1Russman: ^7Sometimes a shotgun blast is the next best thing to a real explosive.",
    "hash_d18a69c3df7bdb8": "^1Russman: ^7Whoever painted this foolish thing is testin' Russman's love of explosives.",
    "hash_d229d9c3e0002f2": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7All right, Granny Romanov, let's see how much boom-boom you've got in there.",
    "hash_d229f9c3e000658": "^1Marlton: ^7Somewhere, there's a Russian doll artist wondering why on earth anyone would ever order this.",
    "hash_d22a09c3e00080b": "^1Misty: ^7Matryoshkas. Monkeys. How long before we get a Meerkat Bomb?",
    "hash_d323215724f066f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7",
    "hash_d33c5131d6ba292": "^1Marlton: ^7Really, the cymbals are a masterful misdirection. Plus, they are so darn cute!",
    "hash_d33c6131d6ba445": "^1Misty: ^7Look at this ridiculous thing. We're all just here for someone else's shits and giggles, ain't we?",
    "hash_d33c7131d6ba5f8": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7This is our time to shine, monkey. Hey, is that where \"monkeyshines\" comes from...?",
    "hash_d3734131d6e9506": "^1Russman: ^7I don't know who decided to hide explosives in a monkey toy, but give that man a medal!",
    "hash_d816cdd6dd9a03c": "^1Misty: ^7Come on, machine -- get 'er done!",
    "hash_d816ddd6dd9a1ef": "^1Marlton: ^7I certainly hope this one does the trick.",
    "hash_d8173dd6dd9ac21": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7This one should finish the job.",
    "hash_d8b9c03fd1fb5dc": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Is it something about the snow here, or would that work anywhere?",
    "hash_d8ba203fd1fc00e": "^1Marlton: ^7Is the snow infused with 115? Is that why it kills them?",
    "hash_d8ba303fd1fc1c1": "^1Misty: ^7Poof! Haha! That's enough outta you.",
    "hash_d8be6dd6de2c40f": "^1Russman: ^7Hope this one tops off your tank.",
    "hash_d8ea103fd21f432": "^1Russman: ^7How 'bout them snowballs!",
    "hash_db12730e98e3f01": "^1Misty: ^7Dangit! Gotta get this ice off me!",
    "hash_db3215bc7acf289": "^1Richtofen: ^7Don't look at me.",
    "hash_dd0d997c2438ab8": "^1Richtofen: ^7Oh, I'm watching, Sammy. Kudos on the headshot. Now, let's get back to business.",
    "hash_deb0dd0d44d3586": "^1Marlton: ^7Crawler alert! Crawler alert! Sorry. Thought that would sound... cooler.",
    "hash_deb0ed0d44d3739": "^1Misty: ^7Got one on the ground. Watch your step!",
    "hash_deb17d0d44d4684": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7You ever seen anything as pathetic as a crawler?",
    "hash_dee9cd0d4505e5a": "^1Russman: ^7Hey, let's have a crawler race! I mean, we usedta have frog races when I was little...",
    "hash_df7a129ffc8c77a": "^1Russman: ^7Well ain't that two licks of dung!",
    "hash_e1000b33c9b651d": "^1Russman: ^7Stu, you listen to ol' Russman and get the hell away from them freaks!",
    "hash_e136eb33c9e55de": "^1Misty: ^7Snap out of it, Sam! There's meat golems all around you!",
    "hash_e136fb33c9e5791": "^1Marlton: ^7They're on you, Stuhlinger! Couldn't happen to a nicer guy...",
