    "hash_ff2a0e9f0a780bc": "^1Russman: ^7Shootin' dead folks with a space-gun. Yep -- this is perfectly normal.",
    "hash_ffca9e9f0afe48c": "^1Marlton: ^7Cadet Marlton of Star Command scores another kill!",
    "hash_ffcaae9f0afe63f": "^1Misty: ^7I never liked sci-fi crap, but this gun is changin' my mind.",
    "hash_ffcafe9f0afeebe": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Aw, yeah. This gun makes me feel invincible! You? Not so lucky!",
    "hash_100882ed8db9ccb0": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Oughtta be something useful in the boathouse. Like...a boat. Preferably with an engine. An engine that works.",
    "hash_100890ed8db9e47a": "^1Marlton: ^7Should be something of use in the boathouse. Nets? Warmer clothes? Frozen fish sticks...?",
    "hash_100891ed8db9e62d": "^1Misty: ^7Is the boathouse the kinda place you'd keep your Agarthan Device? \"Things I Never Thought I'd Ask Out Loud,\" by Misty Briarton.",
    "hash_100c0fed8dbcf21e": "^1Russman: ^7Did someone say outhouse?! Oh. \"Boathouse.\" I was gettin' excited there for a second...",
