    "hash_103666f87f36db34": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7You're a such a pest, Marlton. But I'm absolutely fine with you blowing their brains out...",
    "hash_10396bf87f39198a": "^1Russman: ^7Hey, Mr. Know-it-all! Nice headshot, but don't start gettin' cocky.",
    "hash_103c07f1aaedca4d": "^1Russman: ^7This sure is some weird and crazy...",
    "hash_10495c19336e4329": "^1Russman: ^7Y'know, I bet in its prime...this place still looked like shit.",
    "hash_104c5d1933707ab3": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Y'know, with some better lighting in here, a few carpets, some mid-century modern furniture...",
    "hash_104c6a19337090ca": "^1Misty: ^7Rusty, dusty and crusty. Reminds me of my ex-boyfriend's apartment.",
    "hash_104c6b193370927d": "^1Marlton: ^7Feels a bit claustrophobic in here, but opening the doors helps.",
    "hash_109fabf84107b8a8": "^1Russman: ^7Russman's just glad to be movin' out and about in the world again! Bein' cooped up in that freezer sure played havok with the ol' joints!",
