    "hash_174a047c627d0821": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Can't...move! What the actual fudge?!",
    "hash_174d329bdf965dd0": "^1Misty: ^7Hey, meat-heads...! I got somethin' for ya...!",
    "hash_174d339bdf965f83": "^1Marlton: ^7Quote: \"Speak softly and carr",
    "hash_174d419bdf96774d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7And now back to business...",
    "hash_1751bb08422b5b65": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Alrighty, just gotta stay focused and sharp-eyed here. I've got a chance to finally end this friggin' nightmare...",
    "hash_17572c9bdf9ea823": "^1Russman: ^7Fresh-baked whupass.",
    "hash_17688abd5fe2d7db": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Oh, Misty...I know what you're talking about. In some ways it felt like I was asleep for YEARS, but in others, it felt like I just BLINKED!",
    "hash_17733d7f1c965ed6": "^1Marlton: ^7Very well. I'll take it. But earplugs and safety glasses would have been appreciated.",
    "hash_17733e7f1c966089": "^1Misty: ^7Fellas, you're gonna want to stay out of my field of fire, y'hear?",
    "hash_1773477f1c966fd4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Oh, the big action-hero gun! \"Stuhlinger 2 -- this time it's personal.\"",
    "hash_1776cc7f1c9987aa": "^1Russman: ^7Hey, Marlton, ya wanna see what too much gun for you looks like?",
    "hash_177a5ccb2d075a32": "^1Richtofen: ^7How about you catch your breath first?",
    "hash_1796d85a4ee770b1": "Press ^3[{+smoke}]^7 to switch to shield",
    "zm_orange/location_gangway": "Gangway",
    "hash_17af2e2ebc75a206": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 to open the Vault",
    "hash_17b09ec2dd8ba6a5": "^1Russman: ^7Now this here's a grown man's knife!",
    "hash_17ca2bfc4bbd3f10": "^1Misty: ^7What is this, a football painted like someone's grandma...?",
    "hash_17ca2cfc4bbd40c3": "^1Marlton: ^7Ingenious! A traditional matryoshka doll, reconfigured as a cluster bomb! Diabolical...",
    "hash_17ca3afc4bbd588d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7These nested dolls are a coded message -- a reminder that the world is hollow, and there's another world inside. No, seriously, I read it on the Internet.",
    "hash_17d425fc4bc58963": "^1Russman: ^7What the ever-livin' Hell is this? A Russian bomb?",
    "hash_17df1dc923a1227d": "^1Misty: ^7I love how they come out all blingy'n'stuff.",
