    "hash_188b9c760aab3613": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Nice headshot, Marlton. Now do it again. This time, on purpose.",
    "hash_188ba9760aab4c2a": "^1Misty: ^7Damn, Marlton, I think those shootin' lessons paid off!",
    "zm_orange/location_sunken_path": "Sunken Path",
    "hash_18cb4b9ce55da2d6": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7So...freaking...cold it almost burns! How's that even possible?",
    "hash_18d5cbc3a337f042": "�%�hQ���/°��\u001b8/.pE",
    "hash_18dcf44bdd7a747c": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to give the Seal of Duality",
    "hash_18ed096e53d2338c": "�E�.Se�4F\f�˗J�;-1�B����u\b��+\u0003��0ٍY\"g\u0010].Z�K�n�you'd probably turn my lips to dust or somethin'.",
    "hash_18ed0a6e53d2353f": "�\u0005�(�0\\\u0017Q��I\u0016\u000f;!t�\u0013Ɋ*�\u0010\b�C�\u0013Q\u00178��\u001eH∵3ٽ���+�tifact actually likes Marlton Johnson!",
    "hash_18ed106e53d23f71": "��\u001d\u001d�K�'�\u0003�=~\u0001�;",
    "hash_18f7836e53db575f": "�ҷ��ӥNЛ \u001fo\u0010�fZ�c��NS ^Ò�/���4��\u0018a&�oaܮ��[+? you're my girl!",
    "hash_191eaaaa29f4f90a": "^1Hermit: ^7<sing \"La\" in the note of G>",
    "hash_194fa61f3841f89e": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7What are these weird shipping containers? And what the heck were they shipping?",
    "hash_195c59acf171a445": "^1Samantha: ^7It's cold here! Come get warm...",
    "hash_1970ca171945c388": "^1Russman: ^7Get back here right now, Box! You done took my money!",
    "hash_197b4117194ee242": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Running out on me, huh? I suspected you might!",
    "hash_197b4317194ee5a8": "^1Marlton: ^7How many times have you absconded with my capital? I've lost count -- and I can count pretty high.",
    "hash_197b4417194ee75b": "^1Misty: ^7You know what I hate? A box that laughs at its own jokes.",
    "hash_197c6eadba2f1b6e": "^1Richtofen: ^7Me, too, Sammy -- like all of our sacrifices are about to pay off.",
    "hash_197ea4d47b304c81": "^1Russman: ^7This here sure looks fancy -- and deadly! Russman approves.",
    "hash_1981a2d47b327ef2": "^1Misty: ^7Least this should be quiet -- the dumb goons won't even hear it coming!",
    "hash_1981a3d47b3280a5": "^1Marlton: ^7Wow! Crossbows have really increased in complexity over the years!",
    "hash_1981a5d47b32840b": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Marlton said the front bit is called a cocking stirrup. Why would anyone want to put their...  Oh hang on. I got it all wrong!",
    "zm_orange/location_security_lobby": "Security Lobby",
    "hash_19b54fbe387d2792": "^1Russman: ^7Even if Russman could think of the fun times, he'd only be reminded that they ain't ever comin' back.",
    "hash_19dff28089672c83": "^1Russman: ^7Y'know, I bet in its prime...this place still looked like crud.",
    "hash_1a110daf141443b2": "^1Russman: ^7Russman's probably forgotten more weird stuff from Broken Arrow than he can remember, but he knows for sure they was messin' with that darn Element. Maybe all this business got somethin' to do with this \"Device.\"",
    "hash_1a11fe21d51fde99": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 for Dynamite Bomb [Cost: &&1]",
    "hash_1a1d33ea3d622fa0": "^1Russman: ^7Well ain't this the biggest damn porch I ever saw? All it needs is a rockin' chair.",
    "hash_1a1e29920a655055": "Press ^3[{+attack}]^7 to Fire Flamethrower\nPress ^3[{+speed_throw}]^7 or ^3[{+melee}]^7 to Blast Vent\nPress ^3[{+weapoffhandspecial}]^7 for Infernal Tempest",
    "hash_1a21f0f53a89b43b": "^1Marlton: ^7There does seem to be a pattern to our lives, Misty. Things of great import or value are all too often placed in unfathomably hard to reach places...",
    "hash_1a273cea3d6a9370": "^1Marlton: ^7I'm on the doorstep of a secret German lab. What dark science awaits within?",
    "hash_1a273dea3d6a9523": "^1Misty: ^7This would be the coolest place I've ever been -- if it weren't also the most dangerous.",
    "hash_1a274aea3d6aab3a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7O-kay. I'm either on the doorstep of greatness...or the gateway to Hell.",
    "hash_1a52f188e3f4c218": "^1Hermit: ^7This is not quite easy, but you can do it.",
    "hash_1a544c84a5dff0e9": "^1Russman: ^7We're two of a kind, monkey. Everybody laughs at us...right up until they don't.",
    "hash_1a574d84a5e22873": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Back by popular demand: Samuel and the Simians! We're gettin' the band back together, monkey!",
    "hash_1a575a84a5e23e8a": "^1Misty: ^7Here's the plan, monkey: you die, I fly. Deal?",
    "hash_1a575b84a5e2403d": "^1Marlton: ^7Special Agent Monkey, you may be called upon to perform the ultimate sacrifice.",
    "hash_1a65c29f4bfbb348": "^1Russman: ^7There's one on the ground, but he's still in the fight.",
    "hash_1a70399f4c04d202": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Quit crawling and die already!",
    "hash_1a703b9f4c04d568": "^1Marlton: ^7Ugh, they just keep on crawling. Makes me want to vomit every time.",
    "hash_1a703c9f4c04d71b": "^1Misty: ^7Watch that one on the floor. He's still dangerous.",
    "hash_1a7c4f8664a83643": "^1Russman: ^7Brrr. Russman's toes are colder than a polar bear's pencil. Uhh... Why are we here again? I think I forgot.",
    "hash_1aa21328ebd8465b": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7You have to try to look at the bigger picture, Misty! I'm sure we'll get this little job done and be on our way in no time! You can put money on it!",
    "hash_1abc537d81716cec": "^1Misty: ^7Aw, small, loud and proud. Ha! Like me.",
    "hash_1abc547d81716e9f": "^1Marlton: ^7Like the shotgun, the submachine gun trades output for accuracy. The old quantity versus quality conundrum...",
    "hash_1abf96c21a1b3ec9": "^1Russman: ^7Don't worry, Misty. You ain't lost your M.V.P. Not yet, anyway...",
    "hash_1ac317c21a1e4fd3": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Nurse Misty to the rescue.",
    "hash_1ac325c21a1e679d": "^1Marlton: ^7Well, this is a little embarrassing, but I'm glad it's you and not those two jerks.",
    "hash_1ac64d7d8179b73f": "^1Russman: ^7If you was a General, you'd be Napoleon -- all stubby an' bossy. Russman's more in the market for an Eisenhower...",
    "hash_1af625c7e4ea43bc": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Man, could I use a hot shower. But I'm a gentleman, so...Misty first!",
    "hash_1af62bc7e4ea4dee": "^1Marlton: ^7Oh. *shudders* This is bringing back some...difficult memories from middle school.",
    "hash_1af62cc7e4ea4fa1": "^1Misty: ^7Hey, look! Clean towels! Or at least they were clean 20 years ago...",
    "hash_1af9aac7e4ed5b92": "^1Russman: ^7Anyone seen where they keep the towels? How 'bout some soap?",
    "hash_1b00229a5eb94332": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to pick up soup ingredient",
    "hash_1b01f78df9b2f107": "^1Marlton: ^7It would be wrong to assume, but I would at least hope for a return to a normal, stable, functioning society. With no zombies.",
    "hash_1b18278ca92144b1": "^1Russman: ^7Thundergun? Shoulda called it tornado-gun!",
    "hash_1b1ba58ca92450a2": "^1Misty: ^7Hurricane Misty, comin' through!",
    "hash_1b1ba68ca9245255": "^1Marlton: ^7At last, I'm almost as big a blowhard as Stuhlinger.",
    "hash_1b1ba88ca92455bb": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Finally! A weapon for those of us who can't aim for shit!",
    "hash_1b26bc1db96bf03d": "^1Russman: ^7Hey, Stu! You got some cash you can spot me? I'm a little light.",
    "hash_1b2a251db96ed87f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7You know how they say you'll pay anything to stay alive? It's true.",
    "hash_1b2a2a1db96ee0fe": "^1Misty: ^7I'll be back when my wallet's not so empty.",
    "hash_1b2a2b1db96ee2b1": "^1Marlton: ^7Oh, I hope Misty doesn't see how impoverished I am.",
    "hash_1b398323f0dbec32": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Russman, buddy, you're in a bad spot!",
    "hash_1b398523f0dbef98": "^1Marlton: ^7I calculate Russman will succumb in seconds if he does not relocate.",
    "hash_1b398623f0dbf14b": "^1Misty: ^7They sure seem to like Russman. Maybe cuz he smells like them...?",
    "hash_1b3cc2daa6e75c80": "^1Misty: ^7\"Tactical rifle.\" Sounds so...military. But that's okay, 'cause I know how to soldier up.",
    "hash_1b3cc3daa6e75e33": "^1Marlton: ^7Finally! A rifle for the discerning gentleman with a horde of flesh-eaters to de-animate.",
    "hash_1b3cd1daa6e775fd": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Tactical rifle. I had a tactical kilt back in the day. Chicks loved it.",
    "hash_1b473cdaa6f08053": "^1Russman: ^7Some sorta jumped-up huntin' rifle. Well, there's plenty to hunt here.",
    "hash_1b4f2840b6e36c90": "^1Misty: ^7You worked for Broken Arrow, Russman. Sooner or later, that experience has to come in handy -- maybe even save our lives.",
    "hash_1b5944f15dd0d288": "^1Russman: ^7This here -- the back of the boat? That's where they usually put the important stuff.",
    "hash_1b63bbf15dd9f142": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7How many sailors were on this thing when all Hell broke loose? Yeesh...",
    "hash_1b63bdf15dd9f4a8": "^1Marlton: ^7Seems like more of a commercial vessel, but I hope they have a weapons locker.",
    "hash_1b63bef15dd9f65b": "^1Misty: ^7This here's the business end of the ship -- engines, rudder and so forth.",
    "hash_1b75a3705bfd446b": "Get to the Lighthouse Station!",
    "hash_1b9127fdffd6e3f8": "^1Russman: ^7Oh, I recognize you, Mark II. We got us some history.",
    "hash_1b9b1efdffdf2932": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Ahhh, you slipped up, Box. This isn't Earth tech. You're working for the Lizard People, aren't ya?",
    "hash_1b9b20fdffdf2c98": "^1Marlton: ^7Snazzy mid-century proto-retro-redux design! A timeless classic.",
    "hash_1b9b21fdffdf2e4b": "^1Misty: ^7I don't know if this is better than a normal gun, but I feel ten feet tall when I'm shooting one.",
    "hash_1bbc39b3389a1f34": "^1Russman: ^7Aw, this ain't good. No good at all!",
    "hash_1bc628b338a256d6": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Shit! I'm caught in the ice!",
    "hash_1bc632b338a267d4": "^1Marlton: ^7I knew this would happen! Marlton the popcicle!",
    "hash_1bc633b338a26987": "^1Misty: ^7Dammit! Gotta get this ice off me!",
    "zmweapon/ww_freezegun_t8": "Winter's Howl",
    "hash_1c0690a731d0319b": "\u0015�M�J��n���\u001aG\u0015�\u001eT�_\r%���;G�%��z�AqV>U�\u001d*^�\ah9��-��7[R��ˀq�5=��\u0004}\\�N�]�q�!AY�O�S�\u0002%i��g9r\tu���:m������g�ad she's on our side.",
    "hash_1c085e4db0b218f9": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 for Zombie Shield",
    "hash_1c08637b6703de50": "�%�hQ���/®ː��/�b�\u0013HȰ�-\u0001��mc�\u00174��Z\"���4�[��.� and running? Come see me!",
    "hash_1c18b01251834721": "^1Russman: ^7Russman's gonna need more bullets real soon.",
    "hash_1c1c2e1251865312": "^1Misty: ^7Dammit. Runnin' outta bullets and I've got plenty more brains to splat!",
    "hash_1c1c2f12518654c5": "^1Marlton: ^7Ah, the inverse ratio of weight to ammunition tells me I'M RUNNING OUT OF AMMO!",
    "hash_1c1c31125186582b": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Y'know the ammo-industrial complex designs these things to blow through their product...",
    "hash_1c2b8784bb8aa590": "Upcoming Rush: Beach",
    "hash_1c356afe160c9b7a": "Max Ammo",
    "hash_1c6212f5aff79380": "Extra Snowballs",
    "hash_1c706ebbce21e76c": "^1Misty: ^7This little box just feels wrong. You know what I'm saying? CREE-EE-PEE.",
    "hash_1c706fbbce21e91f": "^1Marlton: ^7\"Haunted music box bomb.\" Four words that should not be strung together.",
    "hash_1c7075bbce21f351": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7So, Ricky...the ghost-girl...she's what? Your little sister?",
    "hash_1c728bc5a555de5b": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to rotate the Zipline into position",
    "hash_1c7a68bbce2a31bf": "^1Russman: ^7This li'l box just feels...evil. Even the rot-gobblers can sense it.",
    "hash_1c7cb6d7b8d04bd6": "^1Nikolai: ^7Congratulations on still being alive, comrades! You have met man in lighthouse, yes?",
    "hash_1c8ad765cd7d9320": "^1Russman: ^7The scope makes Russman think this is just a glorified sniper rifle, right?",
    "hash_1c8fdcd49dc6019c": "^1Apothicon Blood: ^7Skull, where feet slip.",
    "hash_1c90be4081261de3": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 to Zipline to &&1",
    "hash_1c94e065cd85f6f0": "^1Marlton: ^7This looks like a dream come true! Assuming you dream about electricity.",
    "hash_1c94e165cd85f8a3": "^1Misty: ^7This is either really dangerous, or really useless. Guess we'll find out.",
    "hash_1c94ee65cd860eba": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Are those...lightbulbs on the side?!",
    "hash_1cba478a3a2ba155": "Ragnarok DG-5",
    "hash_1cc5498638bd34b0": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I'm up to my neck in dead meat over here--!",
    "hash_1cc5578638bd4c7a": "^1Marlton: ^7At this range, the stench is overwhelming.",
    "hash_1cc5588638bd4e2d": "^1Misty: ^7Shit! I let 'em flank me.",
    "hash_1cc63d50dbd08da7": "Break Freeze Faster",
    "hash_1cc8d68638c05a1e": "^1Russman: ^7No wonder nobody comes here -- it's too damn crowded!",
    "hash_1d0e45476161abb0": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to put soup ingredients in the pot",
    "hash_1d3f997e761afe7e": "^1Misty: ^7Marlton, move your butt away from them!",
    "hash_1d49e70b36bea98c": "^1Russman: ^7\"C.Y.B.\" Cover your butt. That's rule number one. And Russman's got a lot to cover.",
    "hash_1d50582fcd0aa13d": "^1Russman: ^7I'm fixin' to run outta ammo if I don't watch it.",
    "hash_1d53c12fcd0d897f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I don't like how light my gun's starting to feel...",
    "hash_1d53c62fcd0d91fe": "^1Misty: ^7There aren't enough bullets in the world for this! Definitely not enough in my gun.",
    "hash_1d53c72fcd0d93b1": "^1Marlton: ^7I could really use a few more clips of ammo. That's what they call them, right? \"Clips\"?",
    "hash_1d8e6028e7de2658": "^1Hermit: ^7You can do this one in your sleep, my friend.",
    "hash_1d97a2b1e8be1dc9": "^1Russman: ^7Least you don't weigh much. Russman almost threw his back out helpin' Stuhlinger get up.",
    "hash_1d9b23b1e8c12ed3": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Y'know, I dreamt I saved your life and you kept your mouth shut for a week. It was a good dream...",
    "hash_1d9b30b1e8c144ea": "^1Misty: ^7Get up, baby-boy -- before the others see you like this.",
    "hash_1dd68872a158d43b": "Get to the Forecastle!",
    "hash_1df39ddf794932eb": "^1Russman: ^7Calm down, Marlton. We're gonna be okay. Listen to Russman. He knows what he's talkin' about...and even if he don't? He'll say it with a whole lot more truth than anyone else.",
    "hash_1e1bf447950e7c92": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to give Blue Rock",
    "hash_1e4b3cfadcf8b3dc": "^1Russman: ^7Hrm. I usedta be smarter than this. I think. So hard to remember...",
    "hash_1e4fd39c337c04e9": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Brother, are you a sight for sore eyes! You are, by the way.",
    "hash_1e4fdc9c337c1434": "^1Misty: ^7Sorry to trouble you like that, Russ. I'll try to stay on my feet now...",
    "hash_1e4fdd9c337c15e7": "^1Marlton: ^7So does this mean you'll finally start being nice to me? I didn't think so.",
    "hash_1e5545fadd0117ac": "^1Marlton: ^7Once again, I must resort to personal pep-talks to boost my self-esteem.",
    "hash_1e5546fadd01195f": "^1Misty: ^7Well that didn't work.",
    "hash_1e554bfadd0121de": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7This is almost as bad as that one time a mosquito stung my balls. So... ITCHY.",
    "zm_orange/location_frozen_crevasse": "Frozen Crevasse",
    "hash_1e71a1e0f963dca4": "^1Misty: ^7",
    "hash_1e782c8a8d02b755": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Ahhhhhhhh!",
