    "hash_2d3c0ce59b964a2e": "^1Nikolai: ^7At last! Public address system is on. This is Nikolai Belinski of Red Army.",
    "hash_2d46d654a916fb18": "^1Russman: ^7All them blue propane tank-lookin' things. That's that one-one-five shit, ain't it?",
    "hash_2d4d7bcd7dab06b2": "^1Nikolai: ^7Child has been through much. Now, with every strike, she purges darkness. Help her...as she helps you.",
    "hash_2d514d54a92019d2": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7What would it take to get locked up in here, considering the whole place is a war crime?",
