    "hash_34f5fd0465acad30": "^1Marlton: ^7Maybe if I put my shirt in it'll spin out a winter coat.",
    "hash_34f5fe0465acaee3": "^1Misty: ^7If the Russians or Germans made this, why didn't those guys",
    "hash_34f60b0465acc4fa": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Like a microwave -- only for guns instead of frozen burritos.",
    "hash_3529d47579721fb9": "^1Russman: ^7Much appreciated, wall.",
    "hash_352d5575797530c3": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7At least you don't need a fucking manual to use this thing. Marlton, do not start trying to explain it to me...",
    "hash_352d6275797546da": "^1Misty: ^7Come to Misty!",
    "hash_352d63757975488d": "^1Marlton: ^7Needs must when the devil drives!",
    "zombie/ray_gun_upgraded": "Porter's X2 Ray Gun",
    "hash_35415ea5c4f005dc": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7We did it! Let's celebrate! Who wants a beer? I mean, I don't have one -- but I could use one. Or three.",
    "hash_354164a5c4f0100e": "^1Marlton: ^7Results: positive.",
