    "hash_35905a7ccf1096a6": "^1Marlton: ^7As the saying goes -- any port in a storm!",
    "hash_35905b7ccf109859": "^1Misty: ^7Let's go break some heads.",
    "hash_3590647ccf10a7a4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hey, Russman! Buddy! Look what I'm packin' now. Way-hey-hey!!",
    "hash_3593e97ccf13bf7a": "^1Russman: ^7Russman's back in action.",
    "hash_359bb5bd20de3ca5": "^1Russman: ^7You oughtta learn some respect!",
    "hash_359e718115426b2f": "^1Misty: ^7",
    "hash_359f33bd20e14896": "^1Misty: ^7I'd love to kill you all with a knife, if I could.",
    "hash_359f34bd20e14a49": "^1Marlton: ^7This is just...barbaric!",
    "hash_359f3ebd20e15b47": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Mess with the Stuhl, get the horns! Did that work? I'm trying these out.",
    "hash_35c0310b57ef12a0": "^1Russman: ^7OWW! MY BACK! Wasn't even that heavy...",
    "hash_35ca3a0b57f77670": "^1Marlton: ^7Considering our precarious predicament we should collect anything that could be re-purposed!",
    "hash_35ca3b0b57f77823": "^1Misty: ^7I don't know what this is -- but it's mine now.",
    "hash_35ca480b57f78e3a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7This looks promising. Like it promises to be more junk in my pocket.",
    "hash_35e0b2b4adc3a3e7": "^1Samantha: ^7Killing you purifies me!",
    "hash_35e88f3c6a08fd6a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Don't you die, Russman. Who's gonna blow stuff up if you're not around?",
    "hash_3601921f57ca5201": "^1Russman: ^7Russman feels like a kid again!",
    "hash_3604901f57cc8472": "^1Misty: ^7Time to have some fun out here.",
    "hash_3604911f57cc8625": "^1Marlton: ^7Time to perform an experiment in temperature and ballistics.",
    "hash_3604931f57cc898b": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Okay, I can throw a snowball pretty hard, if I do say so myself.",
    "hash_3624a01933da55d6": "^1Marlton: ^7Here you go, Stuhlinger. Just try not to forget who saved you.",
    "hash_3624a11933da5789": "^1Misty: ^7Get up, you big dork.",
    "hash_36282f1933dd7eaa": "^1Russman: ^7C'mon, Stu, get up off your ass and start pullin' your weight!",
    "hash_3642effe9909f266": "^1Marlton: ^7We need a better name for this class of weapon than \"tactical rifle.\" May I suggest \"Marlton rifle\"...?",
