    "hash_3664c4285ded1d1e": "^1Marlton: ^7I am in over my head!",
    "hash_3664c5285ded1ed1": "^1Misty: ^7Don't all of you step up at once! There's plenty of bullets to go around.",
    "hash_366843285df02ac2": "^1Russman: ^7Looks like I stepped in it this time...",
    "hash_369f458680140d79": "^1Russman: ^7Those bombs keep poppin' out like clowns poppin' out of a car!",
    "hash_36a2c68680171e83": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7If this was Vegas, that'd be a stripper-popping-out-of-a-cake bomb!",
    "hash_36a2d3868017349a": "^1Misty: ^7Pop-pop-POP! Oh, that's satisfyin'.",
    "hash_36a2d4868017364d": "^1Marlton: ^7Nested explosives. Pretty darn clever.",
    "hash_36a641a58bec1a5c": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Well, at least I'm pulling my weight.",
    "hash_36a647a58bec248e": "^1Marlton: ^7Wow! I am a legitimate badass today!",
    "hash_36a648a58bec2641": "^1Misty: ^7Man, that was, like, a streak of kills!",
    "hash_36a946a58bee58b2": "^1Russman: ^7Heh. Who needs weapons of mass destruction when ya got Russman on your side?",
    "hash_36aeb1068da5e095": "^1Russman: ^7This belongs to Russman now.",
    "hash_36b0efd7ffc581fd": "^1Apothicon Blood: ^7Asteth, where feet slip.",
    "hash_36b22f068da8ec86": "^1Misty: ^7I sure wish I could buy a nice coat from a wall...",
    "hash_36b230068da8ee39": "^1Marlton: ^7Well color me surprised -- and relieved!",
    "hash_36b23a068da8ff37": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7What say we take you out for a test-drive.",
