    "hash_373c5224ea0e0440": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Listen, if I knew it was going to be this hard I would've just stayed in the cryo-pod.",
    "hash_373c6024ea0e1c0a": "^1Marlton: ^7Wrong again. Maybe my whole approach needs a reboot.",
    "hash_373c6124ea0e1dbd": "^1Misty: ^7That's not fair!",
    "hash_373fdf24ea1129ae": "^1Russman: ^7C'mon, Russman. Can't keep screwin' the pooch if you expect to make it outta here.",
    "hash_376f1740578b8a2e": "Zipline is not in position for use",
    "hash_377129a699c8f229": "^1Russman: ^7Misty, we've had our differences, but I can't just leave you there to bleed out.",
    "hash_37742aa699cb29b3": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7You see me risking my life to save ya, Misty? Don't make me do this again.",
    "hash_377438a699cb417d": "^1Marlton: ^7I have what y'all need right here, partner.",
    "hash_37965aa83750186e": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Anyway! Enough of all this silly food talk! How are you doing, Russman Ol' Buddy? Remembered any good movies lately?",
    "hash_37ab88e00e001f72": "^1Marlton: ^7This component appears to be missing something...",
    "hash_37ab89e00e002125": "^1Misty: ^7Well, well. What do we have here?",
    "hash_37ab8ae00e0022d8": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Oh jeez, are we gonna have to build something outta this? This is like that town all over again.",
    "hash_37aef7e00e0311e6": "^1Russman: ^7Just what Russman wanted... A little bit of mystery.",
    "hash_37c093e83278efed": "^1Misty: ^7Yeah but what happens after this, Marlton? I mean, we hear all this talk about saving the universe, but what does that actually mean?",
    "hash_37f1bc38b64235c0": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Siberia, you are...pretty much exactly as I imagined you.",
    "hash_37f1ca38b6424d8a": "^1Marlton: ^7There is a stark beauty to this place. But I still hope I won't die here.",
    "hash_37f1cb38b6424f3d": "^1Misty: ^7Better watch my footing. Not a great place to slip.",
    "hash_37f3d82b5fcbeab6": "^1Marlton: ^7I think avoiding the frigid waters is probably my number one priority - With the notable exception of ensuring that the reanimates to not...devour me.",
    "hash_37f54938b6455b2e": "^1Russman: ^7So this is Siberia, huh? Y'all can keep it!",
    "hash_37fd226799ad6bcd": "^1Russman: ^7Puttin' you outta my misery...",
    "hash_37fe1b88208b3349": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Definitely need ammo now.",
    "hash_37fe2488208b4294": "^1Misty: ^7Out of ammo?! I can't catch a break!",
    "hash_37fe2588208b4447": "^1Marlton: ^7Gun's empty. May as well be holding my weenie here...",
    "hash_38008b6799b0540f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Sorry, slug, but you had to go.",
    "hash_3800906799b05c8e": "^1Misty: ^7Scratch one crawler.",
    "hash_3800916799b05e41": "^1Marlton: ^7On your way, groundling.",
    "hash_38082e882093a817": "^1Russman: ^7Shit-fire! I am plum out of ammo.",
    "hash_380bac01359895fc": "^1Russman: ^7Come on, assault rifle. Work hard an' do as you're told an' you might grow up to be a bazooka.",
    "hash_3815b50135a0f9cc": "^1Marlton: ^7This weapon has the perfect ratio of weight to firepower. The same can be said for Misty.",
    "hash_3815b60135a0fb7f": "^1Misty: ^7Well thank you for not fucking with me this time, Box.",
    "hash_3815bb0135a103fe": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Assault rifle. Good. Now how about a decent coat? I'm freezing my balls off here.",
    "zm_orange/location_lagoon": "Lagoon",
    "hash_3838aa290fbc48b6": "^1Misty: ^7Would that make me any more real, Marlton? If I listed off a bunch of facts about things I did before you even knew me? Can't you just take me as I am? Judge me by what I do not what I did?",
