    "hash_40654a2e7eb19500": "�%�hQ���/­[R\u000f6\n�}�\n�N��<(�Q��PB4�ן���8𼚂�n{at. I'll trade you for something you can use...",
    "hash_406c183d7157a920": "^1Russman: ^7Well how 'bout that!",
    "hash_4076213d71600cf0": "^1Marlton: ^7Ahhh, yes...sweet victory!",
    "hash_4076223d71600ea3": "^1Misty: ^7Well, how about that?",
    "hash_40762f3d716024ba": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7What's that feeling? Is that...happiness?? Oh, I don't like that at all.",
    "hash_407cc98232081886": "Press ^3[{+attack}]^7 for Onslaught\nPress ^3[{+speed_throw}]^7 or ^3[{+melee}]^7 to Launch Grenade\nPress ^3[{+speed_throw}]^7 + ^3[{+attack}]^7 for Tactical Nuke",
    "hash_40a1e3f6cc17994b": "�E]��R\u0017Q��I\u0003zxz,u�",
    "hash_40caf1c8a46b3dc6": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Why do those things always make me lose my cool?!",
    "hash_40ddcf4cfb7ff17c": "^1Russman: ^7Russman! Puttin' bone-sacks on ice since 2025!",
    "hash_40e7d84cfb88554c": "^1Marlton: ^7Paging Dr. Kelvin...! Frostbite victims, stat!",
    "hash_40e7d94cfb8856ff": "^1Misty: ^7Ooh, you think you're hot snot, but you are just cold boogers.",
    "hash_40e7de4cfb885f7e": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Stopped 'em cold! Ha! Oh, man, I slay me!",
    "hash_40ecadde35ed92b6": "^1Marlton: ^7That crowd on Russman is reaching a tipping point--!",
    "hash_40ecaede35ed9469": "^1Misty: ^7Hey, big guy! You're not letting them surround you on purpose, are you?!",
    "hash_40ecb7de35eda3b4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Get away from them, Russman! I kinda need you alive.",
    "hash_40f8b1314b80b85d": "Upcoming Rush: Docks",
    "hash_41077c72ac687f06": "^1Marlton: ^7Why does this keep happening to me? Wait. Don't answer that.",
    "hash_41077d72ac6880b9": "^1Misty: ^7Well, here I am, sittin' in a pool of my own blood again. How's your day goin'?",
    "hash_41078672ac689004": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7If I die down here, I just want everyone to know...fanny packs are cool!",
    "hash_410b0b72ac6ba7da": "^1Russman: ^7I don't never like askin' for help, but...who wants to get ol' Russman back in the fight, huh?",
    "zmweapon/thundergun_upgraded": "Zeus Cannon",
    "hash_411079232fdd29a4": "^1Russman: ^7Hey, Stu! If you ain't too busy right now, how 'bout haulin' your pal Russman up off his ass?",
    "hash_41107c61cefca1e6": "�%�hQ���/±KC\u000f�_�1E\a`���-\u0001��n�\u0017�\u0012��\u001fh���41�O�+.�are real, right? This is not a trick? Hey, I can help you from up here, but I will need a blue rock that's down in a cave. Hurry!",
    "hash_411ae8232fe63ac6": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Russman...! Wanna come help me, buddy? Russman...? Anyone...?!",
    "hash_411af2232fe64bc4": "^1Marlton: ^7Misty, if you can hear me...if I don't make it...can you please kick Russman and Stuhlinger in the testicles? Tell them it was from me.",
    "hash_411af3232fe64d77": "^1Misty: ^7Marlton...? Y'know how you said you wanna be more useful? I could use a little \"useful\" right now...!",
    "hash_4126fb26ac10d7ac": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Okay, that one didn't taste like anything at all. It didn't even taste wet--!",
    "hash_41270126ac10e1de": "^1Marlton: ^7I'll never stop wondering who actually bottles these things.",
    "hash_41270226ac10e391": "^1Misty: ^7If I can keep from puking when Stupidger ogles me, I can keep this down too.",
    "hash_412a8026ac13ef82": "^1Russman: ^7That didn't taste like nothin' at all! Can I get my money back?",
    "hash_414740170b02b2f8": "^1Russman: ^7Shoulda stayed in the Devil's doghouse, shouldn't ya?",
    "hash_414d8f3f61818b2c": "^1Russman: ^7Oh, it's like I just made my own Christmas present! Jingle-BOOM!",
    "hash_414e49b844f0cfb6": "^1Marlton: ^7I really must reverse-engineer one of these when this is over.",
    "hash_414e4ab844f0d169": "^1Misty: ^7How well done do ya like your slackjaw?",
    "hash_414e53b844f0e0b4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Oh, yeah, now we're cookin' with plasma--!",
    "hash_414f63b0e0420a18": "^1Russman: ^7Who did this to ya, Stuhlinger? One'a your secret societies or gub'mint goon-squads? Nah, it's just you gettin' careless.",
    "hash_415137170b0af832": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Back to hell with you and your undead fleas!",
    "hash_415139170b0afb98": "^1Marlton: ^7Popcorn dog. How 'bout that?",
    "hash_41513a170b0afd4b": "^1Misty: ^7Okay, this dog's had its shots. Next!",
    "hash_415158b844f31f0a": "^1Russman: ^7I bet Marlton could explain how this thing works. That is not an invitation.",
    "hash_415456a7e72b9aa3": "^1Marlton: ^7STU!!! I really think you need to calm down. Can I ask you a simple question?  When did you last see another actual, living human being?",
    "hash_4157983f6189eefc": "^1Marlton: ^7Behold! I have devised a high explosive! And I'm still in one piece!",
    "hash_4157993f6189f0af": "^1Misty: ^7Okay, I just made a bomb. That's a marketable job skill, right?",
    "hash_41579e3f6189f92e": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7What am I doing? Someone less...necessary should carry this. Where's Marlton?",
    "hash_4159dcb0e04b2c38": "^1Marlton: ^7Relax, Stuhlinger, It's just me -- not an Illuminati lizard-person. ...or is it?",
    "hash_4159ddb0e04b2deb": "^1Misty: ^7Hold still, Stuhlinger. And, no, this does not count as \"getting to first base.\"",
    "hash_415b26ee4d82ef20": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hey Richtofen! How do you say \"Thundergun kill\" in German?",
    "hash_415b34ee4d8306ea": "^1Marlton: ^7Did not see that one coming, did you? Because it's AIR -- and air is usually invisible.",
    "hash_415b35ee4d83089d": "^1Misty: ^7Blown away. Heh.",
    "hash_415eb3ee4d86148e": "^1Russman: ^7Next best thing to an explosion. Cooler too.",
    "hash_41b55c1f9d14bb10": "^1Russman: ^7Cold enough for ya?! That was a rhetorical question.",
    "hash_41bd5888984bae96": "^1Hermit: ^7This one is not for the faint of heart.",
    "hash_41bf651f9d1d1ee0": "^1Marlton: ^7There's no business like snow business.",
    "hash_41bf661f9d1d2093": "^1Misty: ^7This must be the most eco-friendly death-machine I have ever fired.",
    "hash_41bf731f9d1d36aa": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Your face. My balls. You're dead. What? I'm talking about snowballs!",
    "hash_41c99db0f6c2ac89": "^1Marlton: ^7At this point I'm just going to assume that all of us are completely onboard with inter-dimensional time travel by this point...?",
    "hash_41d0fb3d3853bda0": "^1Russman: ^7How 'bout that? Russman just stamped \"return to sender\" on a bunch of y'all!",
    "hash_41db043d385c2170": "^1Marlton: ^7I should invent a kill-counter to memorialize moments like this one!",
    "hash_41db053d385c2323": "^1Misty: ^7That's a lotta dead meat-golems. Am I on the leaderboard yet?",
    "hash_41db123d385c393a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7That's right, meat-heads! Stuhlinger the Destroyer has come for you!",
    "hash_421cfa071cd5dacc": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7That scope and these glasses pair up like orange juice and toothpaste. Remember orange juice?! Fuck, remember toothpaste...?",
    "hash_421d00071cd5e4fe": "^1Marlton: ^7One does not have to be a genius to use one of these...but I find it helps.",
    "hash_421d01071cd5e6b1": "^1Misty: ^7These take patience, precision and self-control -- you know, qualities lacking in every guy I ever dated.",
    "hash_42207f071cd8f2a2": "^1Russman: ^7Oh, please. Life's too short to bother with that long barrel business.",
    "hash_4227cbedd2885455": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7It's the next best thing to flying!",
    "hash_4227ccedd2885608": "^1Misty: ^7This is the only way to fly! Y'know, if you can't actually fly.",
    "hash_4227cdedd28857bb": "^1Marlton: ^7There has to be a safer way to get around!",
    "hash_4231d6edd290bb8b": "^1Russman: ^7Russman has left the buildin'!",
    "hash_4233f9d1f88cc9dc": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7What are these weird containers on the deck? What the hell were they shipping?",
    "hash_4233ffd1f88cd40e": "^1Marlton: ^7Hm. These are not standard shipping containers -- not even remotely. Dare I surmise their cargo was alive? Or at least undead.",
    "hash_423400d1f88cd5c1": "^1Misty: ^7So it's obviously a cargo ship. What did they have in these big metal boxes?",
    "hash_4236fed1f88f0832": "^1Russman: ^7Dang this boat's a mess! Look at all these big metal boxes scattered round like coffins.",
    "hash_423ddf1f1bc39137": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to take the Yellow Snowballs",
    "hash_4266781e21f52da5": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 to take the Yellow Snowballs",
    "zombie/tesla_gun": "Wunderwaffe DG-2",
    "hash_42a46f2183d3d8d1": "^1Russman: ^7Aw, hell no! If Russman was meant to fly, he'd have wings!",
    "hash_42a7ed2183d6e4c2": "^1Misty: ^7Can a gal have fun while dead men try to kill her? Why, yes. Yes she can.",
    "hash_42a7ee2183d6e675": "^1Marlton: ^7Oh! Oh, I must be completely insane to do this--!",
    "hash_42a7f02183d6e9db": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Okayy! This doesn't suck!",
    "hash_42bb9cb78e440444": "^1Richtofen: ^7I'm a doctor, Sammy, and I say it does.",
    "hash_42bc8ae30c7f547a": "^1Russman: ^7I'm too dang old and fat to be doin' this stuff!",
    "hash_42c8418d38d4360d": "^1Russman: ^7What's cookin'? Firepower, that's what!",
    "hash_42cbaa8d38d71e4f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Am I the only one who thinks this looks like a jukebox?",
    "hash_42cbaf8d38d726ce": "^1Misty: ^7\"Would you like fries with that?\" Nah, just the gun.",
    "hash_42cbb08d38d72881": "^1Marlton: ^7How in the name of Sir Issac Newton does this mechanism work?!",
