    "hash_42d28ac991eeaa68": "\"�-�\v\u0011�~���[��]�s����a�\b\u0005ByW\u000e\u0010�\u0002�S\t�\\m����\u0016[`��+�$\u0014^\u0005\u0018r�����\u001a�w\u0013�5<Q��I�\u000f�j\n|�\u0010`\b��0b���cW\u0017��E���\u0010�$z�;@�{�maller?",
    "hash_42d28bc991eeac1b": "y\f\b96���=:$\u001cj9Y/�C3[��c1���cW\u0017��E���\u0010�$z�;@�{�maller?",
    "hash_42d46c2121005242": "^1Misty: ^7Hey-hey, Stuhlinger -- you sure you can trust this Richtofen Guy? I mean, why? How? What?! Seriously, what is it that makes you think he's looking out for us?",
    "hash_42dc94c991f70feb": "\u0015;��\bC\u0005��\u001dB[��yb\u0019G�\u001b��y\\�w���\u0017F���t�Σ5�辇\u001d�t5t0150t95:t;! '=01t= zT zT\u0001$7;9=:3t\u0006!'<nt\u00131;8;3=758t\u0004&;71''=:3T3T\ne\a !<8=:31&nt\nc\u0003<;t?:1#t <5 t#;!80t#;&?kkTkT\ne\u00195&8 on: ^7I predict with absolute certainty things will continue to go our way.",
    "hash_42e3987404caee2e": "\u0001$7;9=:3t\u0006!'<nt\u00131;8;3=758t\u0004&;71''=:3T3T\ne\a !<8=:31&nt\nc\u0003<;t?:1#t <5 t#;!80t#;&?kkTkT\ne\u00195&8 on: ^7I predict with absolute certainty things will continue to go our way.",
    "hash_435f386f220fdce0": "\ne\a !<8=:31&nt\nc\u0003<;t?:1#t <5 t#;!80t#;&?kkTkT\ne\u00195&8 on: ^7I predict with absolute certainty things will continue to go our way.",
    "hash_435f466f220ff4aa": "\ne\u00195&8 on: ^7I predict with absolute certainty things will continue to go our way.",
    "hash_435f476f220ff65d": "^1Misty: ^7What's that I hear? We did something right?",
    "hash_4362c56f2213024e": "^1Russman: ^7That'll do, yes it will.",
    "hash_436d3dfc61603b19": "^1Misty: ^7How the fudge did I use up all my bullets?!",
    "zm_orange/location_lighthouse_annex": "Lighthouse Annex",
    "hash_43bc5411ee64cc25": "^1Misty: ^7Hey, Marlton! How do you say \"killstreak\" in Russian?",
    "hash_43bc5511ee64cdd8": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I'm dropping 'em like flies!",
    "hash_43bfc211ee67bce6": "^1Russman: ^7Y'all came a long way just to get killed all over again.",
    "hash_43cbc37ab728289b": "Press ^3[{+attack}]^7 to Fire Flamethrower\nPress ^3[{+speed_throw}]^7 or ^3[{+melee}]^7 to Blast Vent\nPress ^3[{+speed_throw}]^7 + ^3[{+attack}]^7 for Infernal Tempest",
    "hash_43dabbb2b40e3d09": "Get to Frozen Crevasse!",
    "hash_43e8e356cf172214": "^1Russman: ^7Misty teach you that, little man?",
    "hash_43f35256cf203336": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Marlton, I see you're going with the bullet-to-the-head method. Good plan!",
    "hash_43f35d56cf2045e7": "^1Misty: ^7Ha! Marlton got a headshot! You owe me fifty bucks, Stuhl-pigeon.",
    "hash_43f499ab18b58ca3": "^1Russman: ^7Marlton blew its head clean off!",
    "hash_43f7819508fdd180": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Looks like this powered up the lighthouse. What else did it turn on?",
    "hash_43f78f9508fde94a": "^1Marlton: ^7That lighthouse beam reacted to me! Could the keeper still be on the job?",
    "hash_43f7909508fdeafd": "^1Misty: ^7Did that power up this whole place? Or just the lighthouse?",
    "hash_43fb0e950900f6ee": "^1Russman: ^7Was that the power for this whole operation? Hell of a place to put it...",
    "hash_43fbc0ee8b8b5470": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I think my tongue just died.",
    "hash_43fbceee8b8b6c3a": "^1Marlton: ^7Shouldn't this act faster on me, given my body weight and--OH! There it is...",
    "hash_43fbcfee8b8b6ded": "^1Misty: ^7Ugh, that makes motor oil taste like champagne.",
    "hash_43ff4dee8b8e79de": "^1Russman: ^7Ohhh...feels like a red-hot porcupine crawlin' through Russman's guts...",
    "hash_440144270b4051a1": "��\u001d\u001d�K�'�\u0003�=x��\u0013�����\u0019|��Y�-l�����\u000f\u001e5�b�\u0004�#�������\t��iv��$��\u000fmH��}}�\u000e\aM�����G\u0012\u001c.C\u000f���΀�t\u0018�uG���N\tTV�H&��l㸗�\vc`��,٥��J{�musing, too.",
    "hash_4457eb7b0d034806": "G\u0012\u001c.C\u000f���΀�t\u0018�uG���N\tTV�H&��l㸗�\vc`��,٥��J{�musing, too.",
    "hash_4462c9f84493f880": "^1Russman: ^7This oughtta burn 'em to a crisp.",
    "hash_446d52f8449d35d0": "^1Marlton: ^7A ray gun? How positively futuristic! Wait, what year is it now?",
    "hash_446d53f8449d3783": "^1Misty: ^7Sorry Ray -- you're my gun now.",
    "hash_446d60f8449d4d9a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Guess who's got a Ray Gun?! Nobody? Guess I'll have to tell you then -- it's me!",
    "hash_4477f06e174ca3b7": "^1Russman: ^7Don't mean to cast aspersions on a man, but it sure seems to Russman that Stu's brain buddy don't exactly 'Shoot from the Hip'...if you catch my drift.",
    "hash_448caf60d9985bb6": "^1Russman: ^7Current instability?! We been bouncin' around the world so fast for so long, Russman ain't had time or a place to get his darn head on straight!",
    "hash_44a336ae76e06e65": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Oh, did that hurt? 'Cause it felt great to me!",
    "hash_44a337ae76e07018": "^1Misty: ^7How do you like me snow cannon?",
    "hash_44a338ae76e071cb": "^1Marlton: ^7This gun may seem whimsical, but not if you get hit by it.",
    "hash_44a957dd0fae9c16": "^1Misty: ^7So long, you legless piece of poop.",
    "hash_44adc1ae76e9af1b": "^1Russman: ^7Aw, did I pack those too hard? Freakin' rot-cicles...",
    "hash_44c41b6ee90bf160": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7That's a few less freaks to worry about.",
    "hash_44c4296ee90c092a": "^1Marlton: ^7Was that skill or just dumb luck? I'll take it either way.",
    "hash_44c42a6ee90c0add": "^1Misty: ^7Damn, I'm good!",
    "hash_44c7a86ee90f16ce": "^1Russman: ^7Dang! How many rot-gobblers did I just kill? Russman for the win!",
    "hash_44f5ec8ad8ccf185": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I'd give my fuckin' mustache for one more bullet.",
    "hash_44f5ed8ad8ccf338": "^1Misty: ^7Empty. Crap. I'm in trouble now...",
    "hash_44f5ee8ad8ccf4eb": "^1Marlton: ^7Theorem: I'm out of ammo. Corollary: RUN!",
    "hash_44f8b7f1f0338cbf": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Thanks, big man. Glad you got my back.",
    "hash_44f8bcf1f033953e": "^1Misty: ^7Appreciate the help, Mr. Russman.",
    "hash_44f8bdf1f03396f1": "^1Marlton: ^7Bravo, Russman. Take a bow. Just don't hurt your back.",
    "hash_44fd8f5db56ca8cd": "Upcoming Rush: Frozen Crevasse",
    "hash_44fe179e1e8f80ad": "Zipline is on cooldown",
    "hash_44fff78ad8d558bb": "^1Russman: ^7Russman's just gonna take this empty gun and get the heck outta here!",
    "hash_4503e3e5bbc2e509": "Return to Beach!",
    "hash_451c6b486dd10ed0": "^1Russman: ^7That's right, girly, you show 'em how it's done!",
    "hash_452674486dd972a0": "^1Marlton: ^7Okay, there has to be a scientific explanation for her... But I am currently at a loss.",
    "hash_452675486dd97453": "^1Misty: ^7You see that? Girl is vicious!",
    "hash_452682486dd98a6a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Holy shit! I think I just wet myself.",
    "hash_4536c03315e1497c": "^1Misty: ^7Don't know if these drinks are \"habit-forming,\" but staying alive sure is...",
    "hash_4536c13315e14b2f": "^1Marlton: ^7What in Newton's name? That one tasted exactly like Russman smells!",
    "hash_4536c73315e15561": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Okay, that was just straight-up mouthwash. Fine. I can take a hint...",
    "hash_45413a3315ea6d4f": "^1Russman: ^7*BURRRP* Sorry. This stuff angries up my blood sometimes.",
    "hash_45618a1cd60ec6cc": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I always knew Richtofen had cool friends. I mean, he chose me...",
    "hash_4561901cd60ed0fe": "^1Marlton: ^7What is this unfamiliar emotion I'm feeling? Optimism...?",
    "hash_4561911cd60ed2b1": "^1Misty: ^7Sounds nice enough, but \"nice\" doesn't kill slackjaws.",
    "hash_45650f1cd611dea2": "^1Russman: ^7You're welcome to take my spot down here, mister Nikolai.",
    "hash_456ca7d2610b46a0": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Okay, a shotgun's handy in close quarters... I see what you're doing, Box -- trying to let 'em in close.",
    "hash_456cb5d2610b5e6a": "^1Marlton: ^7The venerable shotgun -- proud descendant of the blunderbuss. Hail fellow well met.",
    "hash_456cb6d2610b601d": "^1Misty: ^7Oh, I know my way around shotguns. Yeah, this'll do just fine.",
    "hash_457034d2610e6c0e": "^1Russman: ^7First gun Russman ever fired was a shotgun. Don't know why daddy left it in my crib...",
    "hash_4579e323272ebdf1": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7From what I can understand, Nikolai read the Kronorium, and got a WHOLE DIFFERENT STORY to the one Richtofen saw!",
    "hash_458f54fa14ee17a6": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hoh-lee crap! That one's sparking like a downed power line.",
    "hash_459259626b60d720": "^1Misty: ^7Marlton, honey, you need to get the fuck out of there...",
    "hash_459268626b60f09d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hey, smart-guy! You're getting surrounded like an dumbass!",
    "hash_459899940f28d8f0": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 to give the Seal of Duality",
    "hash_459c53626b692173": "^1Russman: ^7Not lookin' so bright now, are ya, Marlton?",
    "hash_459ccb828bfbb58f": "�}.q�F�\u001f �\u001b����\nOW\tȋ�\ru\b�C���\u00176��YC⶗1X�\u001bP�s�",
    "hash_45c92068b9c8ed7f": "^1Richtofen: ^7Fear is a powerful motivator, Sammy. Believe me.",
    "hash_460a0e86ca1c39c0": "^1Russman: ^7Russman remembers some little ones. They had such big, beaming smiles. They laughed all the time. Right up until when they didn't.",
    "hash_4617ade8995d0958": "^1Richtofen: ^7It doesn't count if you were by yourself, Sammy.",
    "hash_4628a5461fbf7fad": "^1Misty: ^7I know we're supposed to be looking for some gizmo, but unless we hear from Stuhlinger's pals, we're kind of flying blind... In the dark... Without wings.",
    "hash_4663b2d8d09cd0c5": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Knowing my luck, I'll probably snap the rubber band on my first try!",
    "hash_4663b3d8d09cd278": "^1Misty: ^7Come on bow -- let's get cross!",
    "hash_4663b4d8d09cd42b": "^1Marlton: ^7Of a crossbow's components, the \"limb\" is by the most important. If that snaps...? Oh, boy.",
    "hash_466463c5bbac907c": "^1Russman: ^7That there's what ya call the \"dog-whistle.\" 'Cept we can hear it. And it ain't a whistle..",
    "hash_4666a26604054044": "^1Richtofen: ^7You know, you're funnier when you're not scared witless.",
    "hash_466dbdd8d0a537fb": "^1Russman: ^7This sure is a fancy lookin' crossbow. I don't know what half the parts are even for!",
    "hash_466e6cc5bbb4f44c": "^1Marlton: ^7Y'know, Stuhlinger looks kind of like a mailman. Maybe they'll go after him.",
