    "hash_49a38935d0653b93": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Looks like a squirt gun I had when I was a kid. Not as many folks trying to eat me back then...",
    "hash_49a39635d06551aa": "^1Misty: ^7My very own death-ray. I guess this job does have its perks.",
