    "hash_50b34c391522c92d": "^1Misty: ^7And there goes my last round...",
    "hash_50b444ca85d2cb24": "^1Russman: ^7This Agarthan device? Do we know what it does? What it's used for? More importantly, do we know what your German pal wants with it?",
