    "hash_5336201fba9ada0d": "^1Misty: ^7Until they invent the ballistic spork, this will have to do.",
    "hash_53391e1fba9d0c7e": "^1Russman: ^7Kinda takes the...intimacy outta stabbin' someone, but what the heck...",
    "hash_53753033c9262930": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to put icicle in pot",
    "hash_537cf2669cfe8d28": "^1Russman: ^7\"Tactical rifle,\" huh? Why does Russman feel like he's trained with one before...?",
    "hash_5386e9669d06d262": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Well, all right, Box. I'm gonna go show this off to the rot-gobblers.",
    "hash_5386eb669d06d5c8": "^1Marlton: ^7Hm. This sits somewhere between \"assault\" and \"sniper\" on the rifle continuum.",
    "hash_5386ec669d06d77b": "^1Misty: ^7Okay, Box, decent choice. Not so loud I can't hear myself think, and it does tend to hit whatever I point it at.",
    "hash_53894e716f7498b1": "^1Russman: ^7Damn, I'm good! Not sure why, but I am.",
    "hash_538ccc716f77a4a2": "^1Misty: ^7Never bring teeth to a knife-fight.",
    "hash_538ccd716f77a655": "^1Marlton: ^7Now look what you made me do!",
    "hash_538ccf716f77a9bb": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Shoulda kept your distance -- you'd still be here if ya had!",
    "hash_53a8a93f6cc658cc": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Feel free to share that Energy with your fetid friends!",
    "hash_53a8af3f6cc662fe": "^1Marlton: ^7Contrary to popular opinion, lighting CAN strike twice!",
    "hash_53a8b03f6cc664b1": "^1Misty: ^7You pus-sacks are really conductive, ain't ya?",
    "hash_53ac2e3f6cc970a2": "^1Russman: ^7This here is a wonder weapon -- so called because you all wonder what hit ya!",
    "hash_53c472bc7a4d9f1e": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7",
    "hash_53ca2504d91158c8": "^1Misty: ^7All these containers that look like a keg and a lantern had a baby -- that's refined 115, ain't it?",
    "hash_53f014fab33492d8": "[plays note C]",
    "hash_53f264ab1e9d9bad": "^1Russman: ^7Oh, Russman knows what this is. It's a hi-tech-death-doo-hickey!",
    "hash_53f4514d440c7816": "Press ^3[{+attack}]^7 for Onslaught\nPress ^3[{+speed_throw}]^7 or ^3[{+melee}]^7 to Launch Grenade\nPress ^3[{+weapoffhandspecial}]^7 for Tactical Nuke",
    "hash_53f5cdab1ea083ef": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hey freaks! Things are gonna get HOT! For you especially!",
    "hash_53f5d2ab1ea08c6e": "^1Misty: ^7I don't know why, but I get a little nostalgic whenever I see a ray gun.",
    "hash_53f5d3ab1ea08e21": "^1Marlton: ^7It would appear to be my lucky day -- apart from the cavalcade of misfortune that has also befallen me!",
    "hash_5402978e2dbb34e4": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 for Dynamite Bomb",
    "hash_540583bade2500f5": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7What the hell am I supposed to do with this?",
    "hash_540584bade2502a8": "^1Misty: ^7I'm guessing this goes with something else, don't it.",
    "hash_540585bade25045b": "^1Marlton: ^7The average household item contains 195,000 germs...so I can only imagine how many this contains!",
    "hash_540f8ebade2d682b": "^1Russman: ^7Might come in handy. Somehow.",
    "hash_542562a51f3d6600": "^1Misty: ^7Haven't I got enough scars?!",
    "hash_542571a51f3d7f7d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7*Gyah!* Saved again by my trusty cargo vest.",
    "hash_542fdca51f4689d3": "^1Russman: ^7Russman's tired of gettin' hit -- tired of bleedin'.",
    "hash_546b9ae85f7a9448": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to insert the Seal of Duality",
    "hash_547c5d900bf67b10": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Didn't see that coming, did ya? I know that because you didn't move.",
    "hash_547c6b900bf692da": "^1Marlton: ^7Personally, I've always prized my brain. You should've done the same.",
    "hash_547c6c900bf6948d": "^1Misty: ^7Nothing satisfies like a headshot. Well...",
    "hash_547f6a900bf8c6fe": "^1Russman: ^7Huh. Guess you was usin' that brain.",
