    "hash_54ac14afcdef9075": "\ne\u0006!''95:nt\nc\u0003<5 s't-our name, rot-gobbler? Fritz? Heinrich? Gustav? How 'bout Dead Meat?",
    "hash_54aefe6bbff4de19": "�}.q�F�\u001f �\u001b����\nOW\bȊ��7 ���\u0013�Ӹ��\u0019�0\f�6X�ǋ+K now the tongue which is forbidden. Bring us the Seal of Duality...that we may cleave to our sworn enemy. We must restore that which was separated.",
    "hash_54af12afcdf1c2e6": "^1Misty: ^7Look at those uniforms. How long have these deadheads been here?",
    "hash_54af1dafcdf1d597": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Been a while since these meatheads had a uniform inspection.",
    "hash_54d039a7a2ebef69": "^1Russman: ^7Appreciate the help, but let's just keep this between us, okay?",
    "hash_54d33aa7a2ee26f3": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Of all the people to owe my life to...",
    "hash_54d347a7a2ee3d0a": "^1Misty: ^7Oh, I could just kiss you for that! But instead I'll kill more slackjaws.",
    "hash_54e4c6f60f186e20": "^1Misty: ^7I swear, this time it was not my fault!",
    "hash_54e4c7f60f186fd3": "^1Marlton: ^7Right. Sure. Go ahead and pick on the little guy. Look at Marlton Johnson bleeding out on the floor. Har-de-har.",
    "hash_54e4d5f60f18879d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Well this isn't exactly going as planned, is it?",
    "hash_54eec0f60f20b873": "^1Russman: ^7w-Wait. What? How'd I get down here...? Oh, yeah. Fightin' for my life is how. Best get up and keep fightin'...",
    "hash_5508222cfb1bee9b": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I've gotten pretty darn good at mowing you down.",
    "zm_orange/location_ice_floe": "Iceberg",
    "hash_550e31ea87db8d7f": "^1Nikolai: ^7Belinski to team: continue searching for components of Agarthan Device. We are counting on you.",
    "hash_552a394ad8eddeff": "^1Marlton: ^7Well, I would be lying if I claimed to have a complete and thorough understanding about what lies ahead, but in terms of general goals? Yes.",
    "hash_552f81c78340aeb3": "FREEZE MODE",
    "hash_55510845aade58b6": "^1Richtofen: ^7\"Hellhounds,\" Sammy. Proper nomenclature is important.",
