    "hash_5663a9234c243725": "\u0015\f�U-��!nger: ^7Ah, the Thundergun. A.k.a. Death by wind...",
    "hash_5663aa234c2438d8": "^1Misty: ^7Well if it ain't the Hot Air Howitzer--!",
    "hash_5663ab234c243a8b": "^1Marlton: ^7Technically, this gun does not employ \"thunder.\" But I suppose wind-gun does not convey the same panache.",
    "hash_5663ad0adcab23b0": "^1Misty: ^7I regret nothiiiing!",
    "hash_5663ae0adcab2563": "^1Marlton: ^7Oh em geeeee!",
    "hash_5663bc0adcab3d2d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I hate thiiiiis!",
    "hash_5663d9bb24f617d6": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7To be honest, what I saw scared the pants off me. I slammed that book shut so fast you would have thought I was a NINJA!",
    "hash_566e270adcb44783": "^1Russman: ^7I can flyyyyyyyy!",
    "hash_566e34234c2d77db": "^1Russman: ^7Russman's fixin' to kill a shitload of skin-nibblers with",
    "hash_56917185158b9df4": "Pack-A-Punch Available!",
    "hash_56b155f8823f2f61": "^1Russman: ^7Every once in a blue moon, Devil Box, you actually deliver!",
    "hash_56b4d3f882423b52": "^1Misty: ^7This thing is like my old hair dryer on steroids. Kidding! Do I look like a hair dryer kinda gal?",
    "hash_56b4d4f882423d05": "^1Marlton: ^7This weapon reminds me of the Bag of Winds presented by Aeolus to Odysseus. What? Everyone gets that reference, right?",
    "hash_56b4d6f88242406b": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Aw, yeah! Samuel J Stuhlinger is gonna crash the thunder and break the wind!",
    "hash_56b96de8840d0d58": "^1Marlton: ^7It's all gone Stuhlinger. Everything we ever had. Everything we ever loved...",
    "hash_56fc5ab8c0878d32": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to open the Vault",
    "hash_570232ac6c0c86a2": "^1Russman: ^7All them blue propane tank-lookin' things. That's that one-one-five crap, ain't it?",
    "hash_5714266157d9b84d": "^1Russman: ^7I've put down rabid animals before. 'Bout to do it again.",
    "hash_57178f6157dca08f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7The dogs are coming, aren't they?",
    "hash_5717946157dca90e": "^1Misty: ^7Fuckin' dogs are fast. And sneaky.",
    "hash_5717956157dcaac1": "^1Marlton: ^7Here come our four-legged friends.",
    "hash_5744931f3f0f04e6": "^1Samantha: ^7Children of death, you've been very, very bad...",
    "hash_57640a655d91f0ff": "^1Hermit: ^7<sing \"La\" in the note of B>",
