    "hash_57bbca0bc965c08a": "�ҷ��ӥNЛ �?Kw &�^�%�S8\u0010K���C҂�ٝ�H���a8���z*� once, but this is just plain weird.",
    "hash_57d47aca62536932": "Zipline Handle required for use",
    "hash_57e5169254c426f1": "^1Russman: ^7Suppose Russman'll just keep ahold of this.",
    "hash_57e8949254c732e2": "^1Misty: ^7Looks like a piece of something.",
    "hash_57e8959254c73495": "^1Marlton: ^7Unless there are any objections....this is now mine.",
    "hash_57e8979254c737fb": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Why is this thing so dirty...? Wait, why did I pick up something so dirty???",
    "hash_581df03792edfe36": "^1Misty: ^7Man. This is really...the middle of flippin' nowhere!",
    "hash_583cccbe883eb5f0": "^1Russman: ^7Wonder what the fishin' is like in these parts? Mostly bonefish and dead men, I'm guessin'.",
    "hash_5846d5be884719c0": "^1Marlton: ^7This must have been a miserable place to work -- even before all the workers were dead.",
    "hash_5846d6be88471b73": "^1Misty: ^7\"Take a long walk off a short pier.\" This sure is the place to do it.",
    "hash_5846e3be8847318a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Back where I started. I think there's a metaphor somewhere in there...",
    "hash_585f8b6c4af0a17d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Wow! It's a bit nippy, Richtofen! Couldn't you have given us the heads up so we could dress a bit more appropriately?!",
    "hash_58644155018ed800": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7We're not just out to help Richtofen -- we're helping out all his pals too! Oh, and the Universe!",
    "hash_5899bd45d0fa47ac": "^1Misty: ^7Runnin' outta bullets and I've got plenty more brains to splat!",
    "hash_58e20f3f65738957": "^1Apothicon Blood: ^7Flesh, where lightning aims.",
    "hash_58efada766ef777c": "^1Marlton: ^7I honestly thought you didn't even see me down there.",
    "hash_58efaea766ef792f": "^1Misty: ^7I'm gonna do somethin' nice for you now, Russman. Like find you a bar of soap.",
    "hash_58efb3a766ef81ae": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Russ-man! You know you're my hero, right?",
    "hash_59685b91059a1cf3": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7",
    "hash_5979dcb633c28888": "Fire Sale",
    "hash_598822dfecf2693e": "^1Marlton: ^7Chalk up another headshot for the man in khaki!",
    "hash_598823dfecf26af1": "^1Misty: ^7Nailed him, Stu -- right in the noggin like I taught ya.",
    "hash_598ba1dfecf576e2": "^1Russman: ^7Way to blow out his noodle there, Stu!",
    "hash_599b22bc487a8d69": "^1Apothicon Blood: ^7Asteth, where thirst dawns.",
    "hash_59c4b1052b566fa1": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to give the Seal of Duality\n[ All Players Required ]",
    "hash_59c6593b11d437cc": "You have dropped your pee jar, go grab a new one",
    "hash_59dfd28f98d8fb71": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to craft Dynamite Bomb",
    "hash_5a0c76fe268345cf": "^1Russman: ^7Woah, Stu! Everyone's got their own favorite fast food chain -- ain't no reason to get yer panties in bunch!",
    "hash_5a30a82554eaefa0": "^1Russman: ^7Them rot-gobblers sure do take a shine to that monkey. Right up until they don't.",
    "hash_5a3ab12554f35370": "^1Marlton: ^7I'd do find myself worrying that the prototype testing may have been...gruesome.",
    "hash_5a3ab22554f35523": "^1Misty: ^7Why does that always make me feel guilty? He was so cute.",
    "hash_5a3abf2554f36b3a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7You know, I wouldn't mind strapping explosives and cymbals on Marlton just once...",
    "hash_5a41c676fecff038": "^1Russman: ^7You keep this up and Russman might actually start to like you.",
    "hash_5a4bbd76fed83572": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Remember what I said about your shirt? I take it back. You...don't remember? Um, never mind...",
    "hash_5a4bbf76fed838d8": "^1Marlton: ^7Misty, if there's a reason to stay alive in this frozen nightmare...it's you.",
    "hash_5a4d3857fd2f1f56": "^1Marlton: ^7Never fear, Marlton's here! I've, ah, been saving that one for the right moment. Pretty good, huh?",
    "hash_5a4d4257fd2f3054": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Back on your feet, girl. You're a pain in the butt, but you're a pretty good shot.",
    "hash_5a50c757fd32482a": "^1Russman: ^7Don't die just yet, girl. Russman would kinda miss that loud mouth of yours.",
    "hash_5a640130ec24a300": "^1Misty: ^7Dynamite. There's gotta be more explosive stuff here somewhere...",
    "hash_5a640230ec24a4b3": "^1Marlton: ^7Watch out, reanimates. I'm packin' dynamite now. That's packin' with an apostrophe.",
    "hash_5a641030ec24bc7d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7So the meat-munchers have the dynamite. Hope I don't shoot it by mistake.",
    "hash_5a6e7b30ec2dc6d3": "^1Russman: ^7The rot-gobbler who dropped this musta known Russman loves explosives.",
    "hash_5a6eb3c92f5874a0": "^1Richtofen: ^7I don't know about God, but I find it amusing...",
    "hash_5a8610793f761a8b": "Upcoming Rush: Sunken Path",
    "hash_5a9af6259ef48803": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7*sigh* I can always use it on Marlton if he sings the praises of sniper rifles one more flippin' time...",
