    "hash_61e30f61e0f1963a": "^1Russman: ^7That was no lady, that was my bomb!",
    "hash_61e58f21a73dcec8": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Why a music box? It's gotta mean something, right? Or are the zombie gods just making this up as they go?",
    "hash_6224ce48d3ce4681": "^1Russman: ^7Heads up, Stuhlinger! You're in a bad spot!",
