    "hash_6232b205ed9f34cc": "^1Misty: ^7I never had a stuffed animal. So blowin' you up ain't nothing to me. Sorry.",
    "hash_6232b305ed9f367f": "^1Marlton: ^7Ready for your curtain-call, my pint-sized Pagliacci?",
