    "hash_6244cdfdfa961998": "^1Misty: ^7Yeesh. Marlton may like these, but the boy lives inside his own head. I'm a little more practical...",
    "hash_6244cefdfa961b4b": "^1Marlton: ^7Oft dismissed by the unworthy, the sniper rifle is the apex, nay, the zenith of lethal weapons!",
    "hash_624f57fdfa9f589b": "^1Russman: ^7Sniper rifle. *spits* I'll learn to love 'em the day Misty learns to button her blouse!",
