    "hash_629b8284da035090": "^1Russman: ^7Promises, promises. Russman will believe it when the Russian actually helps.",
    "hash_629d5fe4a75781c8": "Return to Frozen Crevasse!",
    "hash_62a58b84da0bb460": "^1Marlton: ^7Well of course we'll keep searching. Not like we have much choice.",
    "hash_62a58c84da0bb613": "^1Misty: ^7I'm kinda warmin' up to our new comrade.",
    "hash_62a59984da0bcc2a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Don't worry, Mr. Belinski -- we're in it to win it!",
    "hash_62b0926e311abe8d": "^1Russman: ^7In a tight scrape, this here's the best scraper of all.",
    "hash_62b3fb6e311da6cf": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Swear I feel my phantom toe every time I see a shotgun. In memoriam and all that shit...",
    "hash_62b4006e311daf4e": "^1Misty: ^7Funny, but I've never lost an argument with a shotgun in hand.",
    "hash_62b4016e311db101": "^1Marlton: ^7So simple, an idiot can use it. Which helps explain Russman's fondness for shotguns.",
    "hash_62c44bc338441cdd": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7",
    "hash_62c537f5e7012f3d": "^1Russman: ^7A knife that shoots its blade? That's like bringin' a gun to a knife fight!",
    "hash_62c8a0f5e704177f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Seriously? A knife that shoots off its blade? Leaving you with what? A fucking handle?! Maybe I'm just not getting this...",
    "hash_62c8a5f5e7041ffe": "^1Misty: ^7A knife...that shoots?! Ain't knives for killing up close?",
    "hash_62c8a6f5e70421b1": "^1Marlton: ^7A ballistic knife. Fascinating.",
    "hash_62cd576049ea09e0": "^1Misty: ^7\"Bye-bye,\" my ass. I'm huntin' you down, Box!",
    "hash_62cd586049ea0b93": "^1Marlton: ^7It's the laugh that always gets me. I had enough people laugh at me in grade-school.",
    "hash_62cd666049ea235d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7You coulda left me something. A grenade? A bullet? A half-eaten sandwich...?",
    "hash_62d7516049f25433": "^1Russman: ^7Nobody cheats Russman like this! Well, actually a ton of folks have...",
    "hash_62e6a023ad36d645": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Snowballs. Why not?",
    "hash_62e6a123ad36d7f8": "^1Misty: ^7I bet I can throw these hard enough  to knock down a slackjaw.",
    "hash_62e6a223ad36d9ab": "^1Marlton: ^7My throwing arm, as they say, was never that good, but what the heck?",
    "hash_62f0ab23ad3f3d7b": "^1Russman: ^7Oh, I can hum a snowball pretty dang hard.",
    "hash_633e2d9c39c2b192": "^1Marlton: ^7It's starting to dawn on me. This mission -- the world depends on it!",
