    "hash_6b8d5b6042c3b2a9": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7*sigh* I can always use it on Marlton if he sings the praises of sniper rifles one more fucking time...",
    "hash_6b8d646042c3c1f4": "^1Misty: ^7Just like deer huntin' on the farm. 'Cept the deer are trying to rip your face off...",
    "hash_6b8d656042c3c3a7": "^1Marlton: ^7Sniper rifles require a degree of inner calm and a placid, Zen-like equanimity. None of which describes me, does it?",
    "hash_6b91e507bbf528b9": "^1Russman: ^7Headshot! And down you go...like a sack a taters.",
    "hash_6b956607bbf839c3": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I'm not a violent man, but when their brains go splat like that, I mean, it's just... *chef's kiss*",
    "hash_6b957307bbf84fda": "^1Misty: ^7Least I made it quick for you.",
    "hash_6b957407bbf8518d": "^1Marlton: ^7Hard to keep fighting without your head, isn't it?",
    "hash_6b976e6042cc2777": "^1Russman: ^7Devil Box, are you messin' with me? You know Russman ain't no sniper!",
    "hash_6b9d4462380f82b0": "^1Misty: ^7Don't worry Russ. It'll all come back to you... Unless it doesn't.",
    "hash_6ba406192b2a5b75": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Looks like this is where they loaded cargo -- before something ripped this ship a new one.",
    "hash_6ba407192b2a5d28": "^1Misty: ^7So is that, like, the \"cargo-hole\"? Or is it cargo hold? I never got that straight.",
    "hash_6ba408192b2a5edb": "^1Marlton: ^7Ah the forecastle. Most ignoramuses pronounce it \"four-castle,\" but it's really closer to \"foxhole.\" Fun fact!",
    "hash_6bae11192b32c2ab": "^1Russman: ^7What kinda idiot builds a boat with a big square hole in the deck? I mean, what if it rains? Glub-glub-glub...",
    "hash_6bb2c82e3d258a09": "^1Russman: ^7Come get it!",
    "hash_6bb6492e3d289b13": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I've butchered your kind before!",
    "hash_6bb6562e3d28b12a": "^1Misty: ^7Ooh, that is satisfyin'.",
    "hash_6bb6572e3d28b2dd": "^1Marlton: ^7Enjoy your bisected jugular!",
    "hash_6bdd700a396dc352": "^1Misty: ^7And they say chivalry is dead.",
    "hash_6bdd710a396dc505": "^1Marlton: ^7Thank you, Russman. Whatever our differences, we the living have to stick together.",
    "hash_6bdd730a396dc86b": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Russman, you might forget who you are sometimes, but you never forget your friends. It's me, Stuhl-y.",
    "hash_6be124bf2f8988f4": "^1Russman: ^7Hey, there, little monkey. You love explosions as much as me! Yes you do!",
    "hash_6beb13bf2f91c096": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Monkey! It's you and me, brother -- together again for the very first time!",
    "hash_6beb1dbf2f91d194": "^1Marlton: ^7This is my 2nd-favorite toy...right after my glow-in-the-dark Marie Curie action figure.",
    "hash_6beb1ebf2f91d347": "^1Misty: ^7Whoever decided to give this toy a TNT enema, well shit, I wanna shake their hand.",
    "hash_6bf86b0f11939fa6": "^1Marlton: ^7I decapitate reanimates!",
    "hash_6bf86c0f1193a159": "^1Misty: ^7Aww, was that your brains...?",
    "hash_6bf8750f1193b0a4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Best thing about a headshot? Seeing that light in their eyes get snuffed.",
