    "hash_6c34b13d836f8199": "^1Russman: ^7Okay, old man, these skin-nibblers are playin' for keeps. Now, get up and show 'em who's boss.",
    "hash_6c38323d837292a3": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Richtofen, you're a doctor. Can you get me back on my feet?",
    "hash_6c383f3d8372a8ba": "^1Misty: ^7Well this is fucking embarrassing.",
    "hash_6c38403d8372aa6d": "^1Marlton: ^7Um, excuse me! I am in urgent need of medical attention! You'll be sorry if you need to work a computer or something and I'm dead! Just saying...!",
    "hash_6c4f73a9182c7a75": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Yeah, yeah, Richtofen. I know your people invented the assault rifle. Almost makes up for marzipan. *gags*",
    "hash_6c4f74a9182c7c28": "^1Misty: ^7Now this oughtta help me save the day again. You know, while the boys flap their gums.",
    "hash_6c4f75a9182c7ddb": "^1Marlton: ^7Muzzle velocity: 4,000 feet per second. Rate of fire: 700 rounds per minute. Marlton Rating: Meh, 7 out of 10.",
    "hash_6c597ea91834e1ab": "^1Russman: ^7Well, okay, Devil Box! Kinda nice when you don't try to shortchange me.",
    "hash_6c5a459b2dba00bc": "^1Russman: ^7Shotguns get real interestin' once you pack 'em. *explosion noise*",
    "hash_6c644e9b2dc2648c": "^1Marlton: ^7To say a shotgun isn't precise would be an understatement. Some of us would rather a scalpel than a machete.",
    "hash_6c644f9b2dc2663f": "^1Misty: ^7I learned to shoot with these back on the farm. Started out shooting cans, and then...the less said, the better.",
    "hash_6c64549b2dc26ebe": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Shotgun. Great. Nice to get something decent for my hard-earned cash.",
    "hash_6c83b2c8cbf9b4c4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7",
    "hash_6c90599b649a939c": "^1Marlton: ^7Facts are facts. We are at the mercy of forces we cannot control. So far, Stuhlinger's friend has at least kept us alive. I suggest we attempt to construct this Agarthan Device as he has requested.",
    "hash_6c94544b211a0d34": "^1Misty: ^7Bout time your aim improved, Stu.",
    "hash_6c94554b211a0ee7": "^1Marlton: ^7Mighty efficient of you, Stuhlinger.",
    "hash_6c97028b1777690c": "�%�hQ���/­[SJ�[�p}���(�6����\u0017㷜��H�\u001e�-�;��)� for you.",
    "hash_6c9bc49aea3dbc4c": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hey, Misty! Wrong place, wrong time, girl!",
    "hash_6c9bca9aea3dc67e": "^1Marlton: ^7Try to hold out, Misty! I'll be...I'll be right th... I'll miss you.",
    "hash_6c9e5e4b212272b7": "^1Russman: ^7Clean headshot, Stu. Guess Russman's rubbin' off on ya.",
    "hash_6c9edec0976eeca1": "Armor",
    "hash_6c9f499aea40d422": "^1Russman: ^7Russman hates to see a woman gettin' picked on. Then again, it is Misty...",
    "hash_6cd4d19e0d49859c": "^1Hermit: ^7Okay, I have a little harder one for you.",
    "hash_6cd89638a8c8083d": "^1Russman: ^7I'll tell you somethin', Stu: Russman thinks we -- and maybe the whole planet -- are running out of road...real fast.",
    "hash_6cecd12f0b0706df": "�%�hQ���/ +V\u000fz� 1M\u0001�ۜ�)\b�Sh�W\u0017���\u001f�㖽`��[��{�p! I have something for you!",
    "hash_6d064765e05883e7": "^1Hermit: ^7Here is an easy one.",
    "hash_6d101ea87a79ddf0": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 to replay the Hermit's song",
    "hash_6d16c198d028e995": "^1Russman: ^7I may not know why we're here or what we're doin', but I sure know how to splatter some brains!",
    "hash_6d1a3f98d02bf586": "^1Misty: ^7From meat-head to no-head in one easy step!",
    "hash_6d1a4098d02bf739": "^1Marlton: ^7Off with their heads!",
    "hash_6d1a4a98d02c0837": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Oh, yeah. Just call me Skullbuster Stuhlinger.",
    "hash_6d1ee8b396196b0c": "�E�.Se�4F���\u0003z�//du\u0006`\v��*b��飃s����A���/X��\b�{ks there more to it?",
    "hash_6d1ee9b396196cbf": "�\u0005�(�0\\\u0017Q���\u0016\u000f�;�e�\u0013�ɢ�\u0018����s��\u0012���ac��(��\a�*+bled! So...why is this not over?",
    "hash_6d1eefb3961976f1": "��\u001d\u001d�K�'�\u0003�3p\aƛ\u0010\u00050�)�L\u0002�sD-��Z�\u00066��e*A�a\u0005jh�L���v\u0019{�w)\t\u0014L8ط Y��`5;��>1�$\u001a7��L�����\u000eȺ\nX?E��<i��F�]�a 푲None of 'em looked like that thing.",
    "hash_6d2962b396228edf": "\t\u0014L8ط Y��`5;��>1�$\u001a7��L�����\u000eȺ\nX?E��<i��F�]�a 푲None of 'em looked like that thing.",
    "hash_6d688a0c68887767": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7What am I supposed to do with this? Hide in a freakin' tree? You see any trees around here?!",
    "hash_6d6c381346043b29": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Oh dear -- look at the mess I've made. Heh!",
    "hash_6d6c411346044a74": "^1Misty: ^7It's not the \"boom\" that gets ya. It's the getting blown to pieces.",
    "hash_6d6c421346044c27": "^1Marlton: ^7You see, Russman? I can \"blow shit up,\" too.",
    "hash_6d72b2d24e6d766d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Holy crap! Death by snowball!",
    "hash_6d764b13460caff7": "^1Russman: ^7Well, that never gets old! Unlike me, sadly...",
    "hash_6d7681466550afe5": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Running low on bullets? Seriously? Already?!",
    "hash_6d7682466550b198": "^1Misty: ^7You meat-munchers are usin' up all my bullets!",
    "hash_6d7683466550b34b": "^1Marlton: ^7Um...Misty...? May I borrow some bullets, please...?",
    "hash_6d810c466559f09b": "^1Russman: ^7This ain't no time for Russman to be runnin' out of bullets. No, sir.",
    "hash_6d832285199c5ff3": "^1Marlton: ^7I concur, Russman. In fact, I would say that it's a near certainty. And by near, I obviously mean a likelihood in at least the mid ninetieth percentile.",
    "hash_6d907ec9dd8d82db": "^1Hermit: ^7Try this. Not too easy, not too difficult.",
    "hash_6ddaca27a8e5d6c0": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7This is almost as bad as that one time a mosquito stung my... So... ITCHY.",
    "hash_6dee829f45b4fee0": "�c\u0016��n�'��)�)̉�=w�\u001dR9v��`\u0010A\u001e�B��ə��]'�X�\u001fՋ�<᥯\u0011�dY�c�@�\u0013\u0011ن*A���z\u0013�R���l�JbI�I>{i�\u0010Z����FS\u001bS\b�\u0003k�Fu�\u0018omplete your challenge to get a reward",
    "hash_6e0cbceab229716f": "\u0018omplete your challenge to get a reward",
    "hash_6e614a4a6617b7d2": "^1Marlton: ^7You look even more beautiful when you shoot their heads off! That's not inappropriate, is it...?",
    "hash_6e614c4a6617bb38": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Wow, Misty -- right between the eyes! Do it again -- I wanna get a picture!",
    "hash_6e631f26fc82514f": "�}.q�F�\u001f �\u001b����\nOW��ɴ�+����\u0017C\u0012��\u0018¡\u0010�-X�K\a��\u001f",
    "hash_6e64ab381c96915c": "^1Marlton: ^7Hmmm... We may be at cross purposes, Samuel, but I do not in any way disagree with anything you have said.",
    "hash_6e64b94a661aaa46": "^1Russman: ^7Nailed that muncher right in the skull. Well done, Misty.",
    "hash_6e930083d005e020": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 to craft Heat Pack\nPress ^3[{+melee}]^7 for other blueprints",
    "hash_6eb1ad1de7723cc6": "^1Marlton: ^7There has to be some pattern, some algorithm that could predict your abrupt departure.",
    "hash_6eb1ae1de7723e79": "^1Misty: ^7And to think I actually used to like Teddy bears--!",
    "hash_6eb1b71de7724dc4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Well, fuck. Am I wearing a sign that says \"rob me blind\" or something? Well, am I?",
    "hash_6eb53c1de775659a": "^1Russman: ^7Oh, you devil-box, you instrument of the Deceiver. I don't know why I ever throw good money at you!",
    "hash_6ebab946cc17d354": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7See? It's like I've always said: there's US, and there's THEM. There's the powers that be...Broken Arrow...the entirety of the United States Government...the whole dang Cabal!!!",
    "hash_6ec40afc79ef0070": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7",
    "hash_6ecae13689fbff90": "^1Russman: ^7What's that thing the scum-sucker left behind?",
    "hash_6eced05b46f243a8": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 for Dynamite Bomb",
    "hash_6ed4ea368a046360": "^1Marlton: ^7That walking flambe dropped something.",
    "hash_6ed4eb368a046513": "^1Misty: ^7What did that meathead leave behind?",
    "hash_6ed4f8368a047b2a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hey! Now they're giving out prizes!",
    "hash_6f23fab923cfef5f": "^1Russman: ^7I know Russman's brain may be a little frazzled around the edges, but don't you ever dare question my character -- my morality.",
    "hash_6f2b8fc9115ffbe6": "^1Marlton: ^7Go pick on someone your own size! Hint: Stuhlinger.",
    "hash_6f2b90c9115ffd99": "^1Misty: ^7*Ack!* Next bone-muncher who touches me pulls back a stump!",
    "hash_6f2b99c911600ce4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Come on, Richtofen, you coulda warned me that was coming--!",
    "hash_6f2f1ec9116324ba": "^1Russman: ^7You hit like a gal! A gal with a razor-covered baseball bat.",
    "hash_6f56204edb8df989": "^1Russman: ^7Get yer mangy ass back to Hell!",
    "hash_6f59a14edb910a93": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Sorry, but you had to go.",
    "hash_6f59ae4edb9120aa": "^1Misty: ^7Bad dog! Good Misty.",
    "hash_6f59af4edb91225d": "^1Marlton: ^7Sorry, but this called for more than a rolled-up newspaper.",
    "hash_6f8398f0a1c98171": "^1Russman: ^7I've heard Marlton call the front end of a ship \"the foxhole.\" Makes me wanna slap the sass right outta that boy.",
    "hash_6f858e94ccd2dd76": "�%�hQ���/ +V\u000f�;(t�A�(\f1���*�\u0017R6��\v���\"X�\n�n�up here!",
    "hash_6f8716f0a1cc8d62": "^1Misty: ^7I think if I had to work on this stinkin' boat, I'd rather be dead, too.",
    "hash_6f8717f0a1cc8f15": "^1Marlton: ^7Most of the cargo loading happened here. Could mean there are useful items around...",
    "hash_6f8719f0a1cc927b": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Well, at least there's some room to run away up here...for Marlton, I mean.",
    "hash_6f9fd589bd4e3012": "^1Misty: ^7Took a little off the top there, Russ.",
    "hash_6f9fd689bd4e31c5": "^1Marlton: ^7You know the proverbial doornail, Russman? Well that's him. Dead.",
    "hash_6f9fd889bd4e352b": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7In one ear and out the other -- right, Russ?",
    "hash_6fac1b551033b425": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7What is she? A ghost? A witch? Something worse?",
    "hash_6fac1c551033b5d8": "^1Misty: ^7Hate to say it, but she don't seem right in the head.",
    "hash_6fac1d551033b78b": "^1Marlton: ^7Uh...Misty? You'll protect me if the demon-girl turns on us, right?",
    "hash_6fb6a655103cf4db": "^1Russman: ^7That there is some nightmare fuel.",
    "hash_6fc975bbe7b31835": "�%�hQ���/¸\vQ{x?\nX��HH��-������\u0017���[��\f�\u001fқ;\u0003[n\vfen: ^7Like Dr. Maxis went through test subjects? No...? Never mind, you won't get that one.",
    "hash_6fd8d4b8f93feaff": "\u001fқ;\u0003[n\vfen: ^7Like Dr. Maxis went through test subjects? No...? Never mind, you won't get that one.",
    "hash_6fdaad97d9d28c43": "Hold ^3[{+activate}]^7 for Heat Pack [Cost: &&1]",
    "hash_6ff9c82a464eac61": "^1Russman: ^7Devil-girls jumpin' outta boxes. Sounds like Russman's bachelor party.",
    "hash_6ffd462a4651b852": "^1Misty: ^7That little girl scares the hell outta me, but I also feel...sad for her?",
    "hash_6ffd472a4651ba05": "^1Marlton: ^7Did she teleport in? Or was she actually inside that box?",
    "hash_6ffd492a4651bd6b": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Remind me not to piss her off!",
    "hash_70336f35717ca580": "^1Russman: ^7Well ain't that two licks of shit!",
    "hash_70360c5a4c2cde22": "^1Marlton: ^7There is certainly vast power in one of these. Hoping for a full charge...",
    "hash_70360d5a4c2cdfd5": "^1Misty: ^7Well, swallowed it right up. Does that mean the Agarthan Device is a weapon?",
    "hash_70360e5a4c2ce188": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7You can put stuff in these other than guns? Misty -- look away for a second!",
    "hash_70397b5a4c2fd096": "^1Russman: ^7Pack that contraption, you jukebox-lookin' beauty!",
    "hash_703df8357185e2d0": "^1Marlton: ^7*ahem* I believe Russman is responsible for that screw-up.",
    "hash_703df9357185e483": "^1Misty: ^7What the hell was that?",
    "hash_703e06357185fa9a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Can this day get any worse?",
    "hash_704cec6e36d13961": "�E]��R\u0017Q�Ω�ϫ\u001b�|}C芎�y\u0005���\u0012R\u0012��[³��3�[��s�",
    "hash_70778226dcc1c188": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Ooooh, greeaaaat. A small victory to instill a false sense of confidence...just so we can screw it up!",
    "hash_709a27f82bfd4bc6": "^1Marlton: ^7This vessel must have some airtight compartments if it's still afloat.",
    "hash_709a28f82bfd4d79": "^1Misty: ^7This end of the ship looks okay. So does the front. The middle not so much...",
    "hash_709a31f82bfd5cc4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7The \"aft\" -- the ass-end of the boat. They couldn't just call it the \"back\"?",
    "hash_709db6f82c00749a": "^1Russman: ^7Soviet boat, right? Those poor commies never could build anythin' to last...",
    "hash_70a75c2ae3076372": "^1Marlton: ^7Well, well, Samuel. I guess I am worth more to you alive.",
    "hash_70a75d2ae3076525": "^1Misty: ^7Nice one, Stu. Also, you could use a bath.",
    "hash_70aacb2ae30a55e6": "^1Russman: ^7You happen to see who it was put me down there? Russman would like to have a word with 'em...",
    "hash_70b7abc2102c8d64": "^1Russman: ^7Anyone who wants to get to Russman has to come through this.",
    "hash_70c21ac210359e86": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Maybe we should try this with screws instead of nails...",
    "hash_70c224c21035af84": "^1Marlton: ^7I put up boards, they tear down boards, I put up boards... It's a ouroboros of insanity.",
    "hash_70c225c21035b137": "^1Misty: ^7Just once I'd like enough time to do this neatly.",
    "hash_70d768a738d5667f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Russ, ol' buddy, you still got it!",
    "hash_70d76da738d56efe": "^1Misty: ^7Right between the eyes! You learn that huntin' squirrels, Russman?",
    "hash_70d76ea738d570b1": "^1Marlton: ^7That's as close to brain surgery as you'll ever get, Russman!",
    "hash_70e2a1a770bae290": "^1Russman: ^7Y'all feelin' a lil' sparky there?",
    "hash_70ecaaa770c34660": "^1Marlton: ^7The chain reaction is truly a sight behold!",
    "hash_70ecaba770c34813": "^1Misty: ^7This as much fun for you as it is me? I'm guessing no...",
    "hash_70ecb8a770c35e2a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Consider yourself ZAPPED!",
    "hash_71016e43b6fe0570": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 for &&1 (replaces &&2)",
    "hash_7139d414e0b782ac": "^1Misty: ^7O-kay. Russians sure got a weird sense of humor...",
    "hash_7139d514e0b7845f": "^1Marlton: ^7A Russian nesting doll, eh? Well, we are in Siberia...",
    "hash_7139db14e0b78e91": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Well, at least these Russians have a sense of humor when it comes to weapon design!",
    "hash_7143ce14e0bfccff": "^1Russman: ^7I was never partial to the Russian stuff, but if it blows up good, we're all square.",
    "hash_716f496513ff8e16": "^1Marlton: ^7Airborrrrne!",
    "hash_716f4a6513ff8fc9": "^1Misty: ^7Incominnnng--!",
    "hash_716f536513ff9f14": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Look out belowwwww!",
    "hash_7172d8651402b6ea": "^1Russman: ^7Stick the landiiiing!",
    "hash_71a6d194144fefac": "^1Misty: ^7Sniper rifle. Great. Thanks a million, Box.",
    "hash_71b8bbc563c7b2e5": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Looks like our frosty friend dropped something.",
    "hash_71b8bcc563c7b498": "^1Misty: ^7Did that one just leave me a parting gift?",
    "hash_71b8bdc563c7b64b": "^1Marlton: ^7What did that one drop?",
    "hash_71bb91d3e3e956ee": "Press ^3[{+activate}]^7 to Return",
    "hash_71c346c563d0f39b": "^1Russman: ^7See that? Frozen bone-sack dropped somethin'.",
    "hash_71c9446e1e354cee": "�%�hQ���/°�\u0016��˯1�B`���7b����Pb��ך�g��aߦ�\u0012\u001bh�have to find one, and something tells me these stones will help.",
    "hash_71c9796d307dc738": "�%�hQ���/°�S۫��bM\u0013\n\b��6���.c��\u0012�EZ`඗.8��\a�+�ing. Such...intense...dreams...",
    "hash_71e88ad32ff700f5": "^1Russman: ^7Somebody else want this? Be a shame to let it go to waste.",
    "hash_71eb88d32ff93366": "^1Misty: ^7Anyone want this? I sure don't.",
    "hash_71eb89d32ff93519": "^1Marlton: ^7Not really what I was hoping for. Anyone else want it?",
    "hash_71eb93d32ff94617": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7I don't want this piece of sh... Uh, I mean I want to share this! Pay it forward!",
    "hash_720073fd1562ccac": "^1Misty: ^7What in the--? I don't think I wanna hang around here...",
    "hash_720074fd1562ce5f": "^1Marlton: ^7Not good. Not good! Cave...walls...closing...in...",
    "hash_72007afd1562d891": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hey! Where the fuck am I now?",
    "hash_720a6dfd156b16ff": "^1Russman: ^7That's the fastest Russman's moved in years!",
    "hash_7217f90fdec59ac4": "�%�hQ���/�;��*��0�I\nۀ�8�����\u0017��u\u0019a ��(z�;\a.{�end it up!",
    "hash_721d2ae141b78a50": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Back-slappers! Glad-handers! I swear these freaks must've been politicians.",
    "hash_721d38e141b7a21a": "^1Marlton: ^7At this rate, I'll lose twice my blood supply by morning...!",
    "hash_721d39e141b7a3cd": "^1Misty: ^7What? Is it my shirt? Like wavin' a red flag at a bull?",
    "hash_722037e141b9d63e": "^1Russman: ^7Where's the bone-sack that tagged me? I got a bone to pick with him!",
    "hash_725882c7463aa6f0": "^1Russman: ^7Don't cross me, bonesacks -- Russman's got a crossbow!",
    "hash_7259af547b044ac0": "^1Misty: ^7Now I'm cooking!",
    "hash_7259b0547b044c73": "^1Marlton: ^7This should suffice!",
    "hash_7259be547b04643d": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Y'know, I'm not, strictly speaking, trained or licensed to operate one of these. Which frankly just adds to the thrill.",
    "hash_72628bc746430ac0": "^1Marlton: ^7I sincerely hope I'm not expected to retrieve the arrows?!",
    "hash_72628cc746430c73": "^1Misty: ^7Y'know, these things can go through a car door! Er...not much help right now.",
    "hash_726299c74643228a": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Hey everyone! I've got a crossbow! Should we go deer huntin'?",
    "hash_726429547b0d6e93": "^1Russman: ^7Least this way, Russman gets what he pays for.",
    "hash_727a97bdb01006dc": "^1Russman: ^7Russman likes what he sees! ...er...what is it?",
    "hash_7284a0bdb0186aac": "^1Marlton: ^7Another technological marvel! And a particularly quaint one at that!",
    "hash_7284a1bdb0186c5f": "^1Misty: ^7When you get zapped by one of these, you do NOT get up.",
    "hash_7284a6bdb01874de": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Wow! I love the Ray Gun! Batteries are included, right?",
    "hash_7286c53ebc61e974": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7\"Max Ammo\" would sound pretty darn sweet right about now...",
    "hash_72bc7aad1591ccb6": "^1Marlton: ^7In a more just and equitable world, men with an arm-strength deficit -- like me -- would always get an S.M.G.",
    "hash_72bc7bad1591ce69": "^1Misty: ^7These can get pretty loud. Least it helps drown out whatever stupid shit Stuhlinger's sayin'.",
    "hash_72bc84ad1591ddb4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Submachine gun -- the only thing chattier than that little bitch, Marlton.",
    "hash_72bf89ad15941c0a": "^1Russman: ^7These li'l guns remind me of Marlton -- once they start yappin' they never shut up.",
    "hash_72d47bc0b0b95f04": "^1Richtofen: ^7Stop complaining Sammy. Surely your time in the cryo-pod toughened you up?!",
    "hash_72dca8132fe701e6": "^1Richtofen: ^7\"Thundercrap\"? If you say so...",
    "hash_72e42a7e15a7e49f": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Oh, no, buddy -- I'm not letting you die.",
    "hash_72e42f7e15a7ed1e": "^1Misty: ^7I'll heal you up, Russman, but don't expect me to haul your fat ass off the floor.",
    "hash_72e4307e15a7eed1": "^1Marlton: ^7So, are you injured? Or did you collapse because, you know...you're old as dirt?",
    "hash_72f15a5bbea99ca0": "^1Misty: ^7The hell was that?",
