    "hash_747095eb62424736": "^1Marlton: ^7This weapon is completely illogical. But I suppose the reanimates don't know that.",
    "hash_747096eb624248e9": "^1Misty: ^7Hey guys, when you hear the tinkly music, that's your cue. Start runnin'!",
