    "hash_749a2fcdb9326933": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7\"Light\" machine gun, my ass. That's a lie -- like \"light\" cigarettes and those \"light\" potato chips that make you shit yourself.",
    "hash_749a3ccdb9327f4a": "^1Misty: ^7You don't have to be a man to wield this, but... well, that's it. That's all I got to say on the matter.",
    "hash_749a3dcdb93280fd": "^1Marlton: ^7If \"X\" is weight and \"Y\" is agility, this weapon is strictly lower right quadrant. Sorry, but it had to be said.",
    "hash_749f869699e80e77": "^1Russman: ^7Money?! Do I look like I have money--?!",
    "hash_74a9a33c85d6fbb6": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Look alive, Russman. Those maggot-munchers are trying to drag you down!",
    "hash_74a9ad3c85d70cb4": "^1Marlton: ^7Russman, they are drawn to you! Perhaps it's the smell...",
    "hash_74a9ae3c85d70e67": "^1Misty: ^7Russman, snap out of it! They are all over you!",
