    "hash_74c7c80258b4ea01": "^1Russman: ^7Whew! This stuff makes me feel young an' vital again! It's like I'm 60 all over again!",
    "hash_74cac60258b71c72": "^1Misty: ^7Well, at least the machine doesn't card me...",
