    "hash_7517ceb2207d1052": "^1Marlton: ^7I'm not doing this because I like you. I'd just rather they keep chasing you instead of me.",
    "hash_7517cfb2207d1205": "^1Misty: ^7Uh-uh. No layin' around. We got meatheads to kill and things to do.",
