    "hash_7ffee83143e9dbf6": "^1Marlton: ^7Misty...my hero...my valkyrie...my rock.",
    "hash_7ffef23143e9ecf4": "^1Stuhlinger: ^7Thanks, Misty. Y'know, you're all right -- no matter what Russman says about you."
